\id REV - Uare 
\h Irina rae Fureniro 
\toc3 Iri 
\toc2 Irina rae fureniro 
\toc1 Iesuꞌa Irina rae Fureniroteꞌe Ḡoeꞌa 
\mt1 Irina rae Fureniro  
\mt2 Iesuꞌa Irina rae Fureniroteꞌe Ḡoeꞌa  
\imt1 Ihore Ḡoeꞌa  
\ip Soꞌa ꞌahiꞌe Ioaneꞌa Patamo ꞌumuḡa ꞌahogano mirihiro. Aniꞌe Iesu tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare boꞌaḡano tahiꞌa ꞌahoga. Iesuꞌa Ioane ahiri raꞌaga iḡunaḡano zazore moneo naginiꞌa fureratiteꞌe moneo irina ihonirotaꞌaꞌe Ioaneꞌa mirihiro. Ioane madaḡano ekalesia azaḡaꞌe Iesu mazao firo ꞌahine aduga boro hidinu, eꞌanoꞌo soꞌa ꞌahi hina ze inarazihi rae reiro. Soꞌa ꞌahiꞌe aduga boro zamaḡano zuni zamaze obone giganadu manohuga hiditeꞌe moneo ihoziro ebu nougenouge zeḡe bare ruhibiteꞌe moneo ḡoreziro. Ebu mada ḡonagano Iesuꞌa bare aradu agire azaḡa zu Satani ruize huniteꞌe rae fureniro. Fie gigaruꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe adure iziga zu raha iziga diuḡadu Badiꞌa teite radiꞌuma onamo tuḡutuḡu rae ihoziro. Soꞌa ahiꞌe hari idaidaḡa nunu zu vine ḡoeꞌa nunu hina mirihiro ꞌahine, eꞌe huga niduꞌa ederogaꞌe riḡa.  
\c 1  
\s1 Ḡoere Ḡadaheḡa  
\p
\v 1 Buka ꞌahiꞌe Iesu Kerisoꞌa irina rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa. Aꞌe naginiꞌa nariga fureru huniteꞌe moneo Badiꞌa tuḡure azaḡa ihozoga veize Badiꞌaꞌa Keriso haroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa. Ebu Kerisoꞌa ane tuḡure vigaꞌe ane tuḡure vazeḡa Ioane vaḡe tuḡunadu eꞌe ḡoeꞌa ihoniro.  
\v 2 Eḡe, Ioaneꞌa horoniroteꞌe ḡauḡa niduꞌa rae fureniro. Aꞌe Badiꞌa ḡoere zu Iesu Kerisoꞌa rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa.  
\v 3 Irina rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ꞌahi meꞌodeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe manohuga hideꞌohe. Iniu eꞌe ḡoeꞌa igiꞌeteꞌe zu buka ꞌahi zamaḡano mirihiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa egohauꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe manohuga hideꞌohe, mazaḡa eꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hugano fureratiteꞌe madaḡaꞌe haniteha.   
\s1 Dubu Fuꞌo Aheu Fare mazao Uhiu Ḡoeꞌa Tuḡuriro  
\p
\v 4 Eḡe, Ioaneꞌa Asia habaꞌano dubu fuꞌo aheu fare veize soꞌa ꞌahi miriheꞌohe.  
\p Izidi radiuꞌeteꞌe zu ibite radiroteꞌe ebu vesuꞌu ariteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa mazaonoꞌo, ebu ani kini ehoro iḡuꞌa zamao radiuꞌeteꞌe viga fuꞌo aheu fare\f + \fr 1:4 \ft Viga fuꞌo aheu fareꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡa inaraḡa boro rae idaniro. \f* mazaonoꞌo,  
\v 5 ebu Iesu Keriso mazaonoꞌo manoḡa zu zama roḡeḡa zae mazao radiuꞌenoꞌi. Iesuꞌe zamaḡa niduꞌa hina ḡoere huga rae fureneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, zu rune azaḡa boꞌaḡano bare ḡabodiroteꞌe vazeḡa ibiꞌa, zu raha kiniḡakiniḡa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa.  
\p Iesu Kerisoꞌe emeḡe zamare borofeꞌohe, ebu ruḡa hina haḡaife sauꞌanonoꞌo bohafe vaḡifiro.  
\v 6 Aniꞌa emeꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe azaḡano ohofiro zu Moga Badiꞌa veize gaueꞌeteꞌe dibuꞌo azaḡano ohofiro. Ani niḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa zu gigiꞌaḡaꞌe radiu tuḡutuḡu! Amen.   
\q1
\v 7 Ḡianoꞌi, aniꞌe ḡoze hina areꞌohe.  
\q2 Vaze niduꞌa ubumaze hina ani horoniꞌuma,  
\q1 ebu ani ḡouniroteꞌe azaḡa zuni horoniꞌuma.  
\q2 Rahao habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa ani horonadu niau ḡoinahiꞌuma.  
\m ꞌUguḡaniꞌa hube hune fureraꞌuma. Amen.   
\p
\v 8 Zuhiꞌa Boro Badiꞌa Gigiꞌaḡaniꞌa ꞌahige raꞌohe, “Eꞌe Alefa zu Omega.”\f + \fr 1:8 \ft Giriki ḡoeꞌa ibiꞌa zu ḡonaga. Hugaꞌe 'Ḡadaheḡa zu Ḡonaga'. \f* Aniꞌe izidi radiuꞌeteꞌe zu ibite radiroteꞌe ebu vesuꞌu ariteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa.   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ioane mazao Fureraro  
\p
\v 9 Eḡe, Ioaneꞌe zae nego. Iesu uꞌano e zae teite aduga hideꞌohe, ebu Iesuꞌa zuhiꞌafiꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano zae teite tiburu radiuꞌohe, ebu zae teite zamahe obone gigane huneꞌohe. E Badiꞌa ḡoere zu Iesuꞌa rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa haramiro ꞌahine, vazeꞌa obohe teadu Patamo ꞌumuḡano tuḡuhiro.  
\v 10 Zuhiꞌa Boro Madaḡano\f + \fr 1:10 \ft Iesuꞌa bare ḡabodiroteꞌe madaḡa. Izidiꞌe mada ibiꞌa, Sunday. \f* Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa eḡe rana radiroteꞌea, eḡe ḡaruna ago boro ꞌahoga bigoro agoḡa teige igiro.  
\v 11 Ago eꞌeꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, “Ḡaeꞌa horonateꞌe ḡauḡa bukao mirihoꞌi, ebu mirihiroteꞌe bukaḡa ne boro fuꞌo aheu fare zamaḡano dubu fuꞌo aheu fare mazao tuḡuroꞌi. Ne boroboro aꞌe Efeso, Semurana, Peregamo, Tuatira, Sadesi, Filadelefia ebu Laodikea.”   
\p
\v 12 Eꞌanoꞌo e iniuꞌa ḡoereꞌetaꞌaꞌe ederihi radu tehiro. Eꞌa tehirotene, golo hina haḡairoteꞌe ihureḡa odaḡa fuꞌo aheu fare horoniro.  
\v 13 Ebu ihure odaḡa nemaḡano Vaze Ubuga heuḡa ꞌahoga horoniro. Aniꞌe dabua faḡa ovore oda ḡonaga vidaro zu golo hina haḡairoteꞌe miniḡa uꞌuniḡano utiro.  
\v 14 Ani vadini iguḡaꞌe mamoe iguḡa zu ḡoze heuḡa ꞌuruḡa. Ani ubumaꞌe ire roga duhuḡa heuḡa.  
\v 15 Ani odaꞌe kopa ire rogao kanimaranadu veveniroteꞌe teige vazavazahiro. Ani agoꞌe vu boro ḡuhiḡaniꞌa noauꞌeteꞌe teigiro.  
\v 16 Ani buzuva fuꞌo aheu fare edaꞌe ꞌevoꞌano oboniro, ebu benisi eꞌaḡa aheuꞌa hebeꞌanonoꞌo bua ariro. Ebu ani iraḡaꞌe madaꞌa ḡihau hiauꞌeteꞌe teigiro.   
\p
\v 17 Ani horonirotene, e rune vazeḡa teige odaḡa babaḡano higau bauriro. ꞌOugirotene, aniꞌa edaꞌe ꞌevoꞌa eḡe rana teadu ꞌahige rae reiro, “Ago rihanoꞌi. Eꞌe ḡadaheḡa zu ḡonaga.  
\v 18 Eꞌe radiuꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa. Eꞌe ibite rudaro rehano, ḡianoꞌi, eꞌe radiu tuḡutuḡu. E vaze runeo mae tuḡuziteꞌe ibihetaḡa kiḡa meiro ebu rune azaḡa haba\f + \fr 1:18 \fqa Hadesi \f* zuhiꞌaniꞌohe.  
\v 19 Eꞌanoꞌo ḡaeꞌa horonateꞌe ḡauḡa mirihoꞌi. Izidi fureruꞌeteꞌe ebu vesuꞌu fureratiteꞌe ḡauḡa niduꞌa horonadu mirihoꞌi.  
\v 20 Ḡaeꞌa eḡe edaꞌe ꞌevoꞌano buzuva fuꞌo aheu fare ebu golo hina haḡairoteꞌe ihureḡa odaḡa fuꞌo aheu fare horoniro. Eꞌe huga ꞌuꞌuruḡaꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe: Buzuva fuꞌo aheu fareꞌe dubu fuꞌo aheu fare ibitoziꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa vigaviga,\f + \fr 1:20 \fqa ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa \f* ebu ihure odaḡa fuꞌo aheu fareꞌe dubu fuꞌo aheu fare.” \fig Ihure odaḡa fuꞌo aheu fare|src="bk00154b.tif" size="col" ref="1:12-20" \fig*   
\c 2  
\s1 Efeso Ekalesia Ziroteꞌe Ḡoeꞌa  
\p
\v 1 Kerisoꞌa eḡe mazao ꞌahige rae reiro, “Efeso ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa viga\f + \fr 2:1 \fqa ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa \f* veize ꞌahige mirihoꞌi:  
\p 'Buzuva fuꞌo aheu fare edaꞌe ꞌevoꞌano oboniroteꞌe ebu golo hina haḡairoteꞌe ihureḡa odaḡa fuꞌo aheu fare boꞌaḡano ragaveꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa ꞌahige raꞌohe:   
\p
\v 2 Efeso ekalesia, e zaꞌa nagini haḡairoteꞌe, zu inare gauiroteꞌe, zu zamaze obone giganirotaꞌaꞌe edeḡa. Ebu e zaeꞌa sauꞌa azaḡa mae ḡihizoga mene idaḡa rae raꞌetaꞌaꞌe edeḡa. Ebu zaeꞌa mene apostolo azaḡaꞌe ze zeḡeꞌa bare apostolo azaḡa rae fureneꞌeteꞌe faine udahadu zeꞌe ḡuriro azaḡa rae furenirotaꞌaꞌe zuni edeḡa.  
\v 3 Ebu zaeꞌa zamaze obone giganiroteꞌe, zu eḡe veize aduga hidadu zamaze rinediroteꞌe, ebu mene zorenirotaꞌaꞌe e edeḡa.  
\v 4 Rehano eꞌe ḡau ꞌahoga moneo zae rozeꞌohe. Zaꞌa ḡadaheḡano eḡe zu vaze zamare borofiro, rehano izidiꞌe ꞌuguḡa zamaroneḡa mae modiro.  
\v 5 Eꞌanoꞌo za noumanoꞌo uite buarotaꞌaꞌe zamaroꞌi. Ḡihuroꞌi ebu zaꞌa ḡadaheḡano haḡaidoteꞌe haḡaiḡa haḡaoꞌi. Mene ꞌougine zu mene ḡihurine, eḡeꞌa zae vaḡe amadu zae ihure odaḡaꞌe iḡuꞌanonoꞌo mae vaḡiniꞌuma.  
\v 6 U ꞌahiꞌe zaeꞌa faine haḡaeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa: Za ḡuriro ihore vazeḡa, niḡa Nikolaita hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa duḡuruꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa heꞌeheꞌeneꞌohe. Eḡe zuni haḡaize heꞌeheꞌeneꞌohe.  
\v 7 Iniu teḡaḡota roꞌidene, Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ekalesia niduꞌa mazao ḡoereꞌeteꞌe egoꞌi. Eḡeꞌa iniu sauꞌa ḡauḡa raharahaneꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Badiꞌa meba manomano zamaḡano ḡabone ziniꞌeteꞌe ireḡa maḡa anogaꞌe idaḡa rae reꞌuma.'” \fig Asia Habaꞌano Dubu Fuꞌo Aheu Fare|src="GPS_Seven Churches Plain BW-Uare.ai" size="col" ref="2" \fig*   
\s1 Semurana Ekalesia Ziroteꞌe Ḡoeꞌa  
\p
\v 8 “Semurana ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa viga veize ꞌahige mirihoꞌi:  
\p 'Ḡadaheḡa zu ḡonaga, ebu rudanadu bare ḡabodiroteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa ꞌahige raꞌohe:   
\p
\v 9 Semurana ekalesia, e zaeꞌa aduga hideꞌeteꞌe zu zaꞌe zahara azaḡa rae raꞌetaꞌaꞌe edeḡa. Rehano zaꞌe hube hune maꞌora azaḡa. Iniu zeḡeꞌa bare Iuda azaḡa rae raꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa za rae sausauzeꞌetaꞌaꞌe edeḡa. Zeꞌe mene Iuda azaḡa, rehano Satani mone azaḡa.  
\v 10 Zaꞌe vesu aduga hiditeꞌe moneo ago rihanoꞌi. Ḡianoꞌi, Diaboloꞌa zae tuhuzoga veize, zae boꞌaḡano vaze nu mae ḡuꞌa neḡano feuziꞌuma ebu zaꞌe mada gaubanana aduga hidiꞌuma. Aduga eꞌe uꞌano rune hidoꞌidene zuni, zamaze niduꞌa hina fioꞌi. ꞌOugine, eḡeꞌa kini vadini adiriḡa, ḡabone tuḡutuḡu ziniꞌuma.  
\v 11 Iniu teḡaḡota roꞌidene, Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ekalesia niduꞌa mazao ḡoereꞌeteꞌe egoꞌi. Sauꞌa ḡauḡa raharahaneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe rune aheuḡaniꞌa mene sausauniꞌuma.'”   
\s1 Peregamo Ekalesia Ziroteꞌe Ḡoeꞌa  
\p
\v 12 “Peregamo ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa viga veize ꞌahige mirihoꞌi:  
\p 'Benisi naenae eꞌaḡa meiroteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa ꞌahige raꞌohe:   
\p
\v 13 Peregamo ekalesia, e zaꞌa noumao radiuꞌetaꞌaꞌe edeḡa. Zae radone habaꞌano Sataniꞌa kini ehoro iḡuꞌano ehoreꞌohe. Rehano zaꞌa eḡe ni obone giganiro. Zae haba, Sataniꞌa radiuꞌeteꞌe habaꞌano zama niduꞌa hina eḡe moneo rae fureniroteꞌe vazeḡa, niḡa Antipa maro. Eꞌe madaḡano zuni, zaꞌa eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe mene modiro.  
\v 14 Rehano e zae mazao ḡau nu moneo rozeꞌohe. Zae boꞌaḡano vaze nuꞌa Balama ihore hegoteꞌohe. Balamaꞌa Balaki ihonadu Balakiꞌa Isaraela azaḡa sauꞌa ibiḡano tutuziro. ꞌOugadu Isaraela azaḡaniꞌa ḡuriro badiꞌaḡa dibuꞌoharoteꞌe ogomuḡa aro zu daroe futaro.\x + \xo 2:14 \xt Naba 22:5, 7, 25:1-3, 31:16; Goro 23:4 \x*  
\v 15 Eꞌe teige, Nikolaita duḡuru ihore hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa nuꞌe zae boꞌaḡano zuni radiuꞌohe.  
\v 16 Eꞌanoꞌo ḡihuroꞌi. Mene ꞌougine, e ḡarihe amadu eḡe hebeonoꞌo benisi hina sauꞌa azaḡa ꞌuguḡa teite utitiꞌuma.  
\v 17 Iniu teḡaḡota roꞌidene, Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ekalesia niduꞌa mazao ḡoereꞌeteꞌe egoꞌi. Sauꞌa ḡauḡa raharahaneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe, ꞌuꞌuru tiroteꞌe ogomuḡa, mana nu eḡeꞌa haꞌuma. Ebu eḡeꞌa hadi ꞌuruḡa haꞌuma. Hadi eꞌe raganoꞌe ni iziga mirihoga. Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ni eꞌe mene ederiꞌuma, rehano iniuꞌa eꞌe meiteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa daꞌo ederiꞌuma.'”   
\s1 Tuatira Ekalesia Ziroteꞌe Ḡoeꞌa  
\p
\v 18 “Tuatira ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa viga veize ꞌahige mirihoꞌi:  
\p 'ꞌAhiꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga ḡoere. Ani ubumaꞌe ire roga duhuḡa heuḡa, ebu ani odaꞌe kopaꞌa vazavazahoga heuḡa. Aniꞌa ꞌahige raꞌohe:   
\p
\v 19 Tuatira ekalesia, e zaꞌa nagini haḡaeꞌeteꞌe, eḡe zamareꞌeteꞌe, fieꞌeteꞌe, eḡe veize gaueꞌeteꞌe zu zamaze obone giganeꞌetaꞌaꞌe edeḡa. Ebu e edeḡa, za haḡaize ꞌuguḡa izidi ufeta haḡaeꞌohe, aꞌe ḡadaheḡano haḡairotaꞌaꞌe vitinoga.  
\v 20 Rehano e ḡau ꞌahoga moneo za rozeꞌohe. Zaꞌe roḡae ꞌahoga, niḡa Isebele mae ḡihineꞌohe. Ani aneꞌa bare peroveta vazeḡa rae huneꞌohe. Aniꞌa eḡe tuḡure azaḡa ihozadu ze daro futauꞌeteꞌe zu ḡuriro badiꞌaḡa dibuꞌoharoteꞌe ogomuḡa auꞌeteꞌe ibiḡano tutuze veꞌozeꞌohe.  
\v 21 E roḡae eꞌeꞌa ḡihurifine mada nu haro, rehano ani ane daro haḡaiḡanonoꞌo ḡihuroga mene uratiro.  
\v 22 Eꞌanoꞌo eḡeꞌa ani aduga hanadu aniꞌe uginiꞌuma ebu evane rana baze radiꞌuma. Iniu ani teite ubuma ḡezauꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ani haḡai hegoteꞌeteꞌeanoꞌo mene ḡihurine, zeḡe zuni aduga boro hidiꞌuma.  
\v 23 Ebu eḡeꞌa ani hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zimi ruziꞌuma. ꞌOugine, eꞌe vaze zama zu zamaroneze udaheꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa rae ekalesia niduꞌa ederiꞌuma. Eḡeꞌa zae tibatiba haḡaize idunaḡano naeḡa baronoziniꞌuma.   
\p
\v 24 Rehano Tuatira azaḡa boꞌaḡano vaze ꞌahogaꞌahoga, zae ziꞌohe. Zaꞌa Isebele ihore mene hegotiro, zu Sataniꞌa ꞌuꞌuru hune tiroteꞌe ḡauḡa mene ederiro. Eꞌanoꞌo e zae rana aduga ḡauḡa ꞌahoga mene mae tiꞌuma,  
\v 25 rehano ꞌahi daꞌo reꞌuma: Zaeꞌa fieꞌeteꞌe zu ḡoere huga hegoteꞌeteꞌe obone giganoꞌi, onamo eḡeꞌa ariꞌuma.  
\v 26 Sauꞌa ḡauḡa raharahaneꞌeteꞌe zu eḡe gau haḡae onamo ḡonaga maꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞋe eḡeꞌa habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa zuhiꞌaziteꞌe gigiꞌaḡa haꞌuma.  
\v 27 Aniꞌa auri somoriḡa hina ze zuhiꞌaziꞌuma ebu taḡora ḡoḡoreḡa seꞌeneꞌeteꞌe teige zimi seꞌeziꞌuma.\x + \xo 2:27 \xt Salamo 2:9; Irina rae fureniro 12:5, 19:15 \x*  
\v 28 Ane gigiꞌaꞌe eḡeꞌa eḡe Mama mazaonoꞌo meiroteꞌe gigiꞌaḡa teigiꞌuma. Agire ḡauḡa raharahaneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡeꞌa irara buzuvaḡa zuni haꞌuma.  
\v 29 Iniu teḡaḡota roꞌidene, Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ekalesia niduꞌa mazao ḡoereꞌeteꞌe egoꞌi.'”   
\c 3  
\s1 Sadesi Ekalesia Ziroteꞌe Ḡoeꞌa  
\p
\v 1 “Sadesi ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa viga\f + \fr 3:1 \fqa ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa \f* veize ꞌahige mirihoꞌi:  
\p 'Badiꞌa viga fuꞌo aheu fare zu buzuva fuꞌo aheu fare oboneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa ꞌahige raꞌohe:  
\p Sadesi ekalesia, e zae haḡai edeḡa. Vazeꞌa zaꞌe ḡaboga rae niguzeꞌohe, rehano zaꞌe ruga.  
\v 2 Evatoꞌi. Zae mazao haḡai manoḡa tahiḡa ꞌize radiuꞌeteꞌe inaranoꞌi. Haḡai manoḡa aꞌe nariga rudauꞌohe. E za horozeꞌetene, zae haḡaiꞌe eḡe Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa hune rae rouga mene idaḡa.  
\v 3 Eꞌanoꞌo zaeꞌa meiroteꞌe zu igiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa zamaroꞌi. Eꞌe ḡoeꞌa egoꞌi ebu haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo ḡihuroꞌi. Za mene evatine, e ḡonore vazeḡa teige amiꞌuma ebu eꞌa noꞌe madaḡano amitaꞌaꞌe za mene ederiꞌuma.  
\v 4 Rehano Sadesi zamaḡano dabuaze mene toraniroteꞌe azaḡa nuꞌe zae boꞌaḡano radiuꞌohe. Zeꞌe dabuaze ꞌuruḡa vidanadu eḡe teite ragaviꞌuma, mazaḡa zeꞌe ꞌouge haḡaogaꞌe idaḡa.  
\v 5 Sauꞌa ḡauḡa raharahaneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe zeḡe teige dabua ꞌuruḡa vidoziniꞌuma. Eḡeꞌa iniu ḡaboziteꞌe azaḡa ni mirihiroteꞌe bukaḡano ani niꞌe mene fahiꞌuma. Ebu eḡe Mama zu ane tuḡure vigaviga ubumao eḡeꞌa aniꞌe eḡe none vazeḡa rae fureniꞌuma.  
\v 6 Iniu teḡaḡota roꞌidene, Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ekalesia mazao ḡoereꞌeteꞌe egoꞌi.'”   
\s1 Filadelefia Ekalesia Ziroteꞌe Ḡoeꞌa  
\p
\v 7 “Filadelefia ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa viga veize ꞌahige mirihoꞌi:  
\p 'ꞌAhiꞌe zaḡoḡa zu huga vazeḡa ḡoere. Aniꞌe kini Davida kiḡa oboniroteꞌe teige, inaraḡa boro meiro. ꞌAniꞌa ibiheta vavaꞌine, vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa haranoga mene idaḡa, ebu aniꞌa haraune vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa vavaꞌoga mene idaḡa:   
\p
\v 8 Filadelefia ekalesia, e zae haḡai edeḡa. Ḡianoꞌi, eḡeꞌa zae zamao ibiheta ꞌahoga vavae tiro. Ibiheta aꞌe vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa haranoga mene idaḡa. E edeḡa inarazeꞌe tahiḡa, rehano za eḡe ḡoere hegotiro zu nihe mene oꞌoniro.  
\v 9 Vaze nuꞌe Satani duḡuru mone azaḡa. Zeꞌe mene Iuda azaḡa rehano, ze zeḡeꞌa bare Iuda azaḡa rae ḡurireꞌohe. Eḡeꞌa ze tutuzadu zae vaḡe amiꞌuma. Eḡeꞌa ze tutuzadu zeꞌe zae oda babaḡano ḡuḡuriꞌuma zu eḡeꞌa za zamarirotaꞌaꞌe ze ederiꞌuma.  
\v 10 E za ꞌahige rae ziro, “Aduga zamaḡano zamaze obone giganoꞌi.” Eꞌe ḡoeꞌa zaeꞌa hegotiro ꞌahine, aduga boro madaḡano eḡeꞌa zae biriꞌuma. Aduga boro aꞌe rahao radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa tuhuzifine raha ꞌahi niduꞌa zamaḡano fureraꞌuma.  
\v 11 Eꞌe ḡarihe amiꞌuma. Zaꞌa meiteꞌe naeḡa, kini vadini adiriḡaꞌe vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa mene meifine, zaeꞌa fieꞌeteꞌe zu ḡoere huga hegoteꞌeteꞌe obone giganoꞌi.  
\v 12 Sauꞌa ḡauḡa raharahaneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡeꞌa eḡe Badiꞌa kuru neḡa gadoḡa teige ohoniꞌuma, ebu ani kuru neḡa aꞌe mene bare modiꞌuma. Eḡeꞌa eḡe Badiꞌa ni ebu eḡe Badiꞌa ne boro ni ani rana mirihiꞌuma. Badiꞌa ne boro adureo eḡe Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo ovaeꞌetaꞌaꞌe Ierusalema iziga. Ebu eḡeꞌa eḡe ni iziga ani rana mirihiꞌuma.  
\v 13 Iniu teḡaḡota roꞌidene, Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ekalesia mazao ḡoereꞌeteꞌe egoꞌi.'”   
\s1 Laodikea Ekalesia Ziroteꞌe Ḡoeꞌa  
\p
\v 14 “Laodikea ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa viga veize ꞌahige mirihoꞌi:  
\p ''Ahiꞌe Amen rae huneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ḡoere. Aniꞌe zamaḡa niduꞌa hina haḡaeꞌohe zu Badiꞌa ḡoere hugano rae fureneꞌohe. Aniꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa haḡairoteꞌe ḡauḡa niduꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa:   
\p
\v 15 Laodikea ekalesia, e zae haḡai edeḡa. Zaꞌe mene vu gigiꞌa heuḡa, ebu zuni mene vu nahuga heuḡa. E zaꞌe vu gigiꞌa heuḡa ga vu nahuga heuḡa urateꞌohe.  
\v 16 Rehano zaꞌe mene gigiꞌa ebu zuni mene nahuga. Zaꞌe vu gigigigiꞌa heuḡa. Eꞌanoꞌo eḡeꞌa zaꞌe eḡe hebeonoꞌo nariga furure vazeꞌohe.  
\v 17 Za zaeꞌa maꞌora azaḡa zu ḡau ḡehaḡa meiro rae raꞌohe, ebu zae mazao ḡau ꞌahoganiꞌa ferezeꞌetaꞌaꞌe oꞌoꞌa rae raꞌohe. Rehano za aḡuꞌa, zae mazao aduga daꞌo radu matuꞌu ꞌahogani oꞌoꞌa. Zaꞌe vetuḡaḡa, zaharaḡa, ubumaze kuruḡa, zu firina.  
\v 18 Eꞌanoꞌo eḡeꞌa za iraduguzeꞌohe. Zaꞌe maꞌora azaḡa reifine eḡe mazaonoꞌo ire roga hina veveniroteꞌe goloḡa hoitoꞌi. Ebu zae firina mazagaroḡa ꞌuadu za firineꞌetaꞌaꞌe vazeꞌa mene horozifine, dabua ꞌuruḡa hoitadu vidanoꞌi. Ebu raꞌafine, ubuma muramuraḡa hoitadu ubumaze rana soronoꞌi.  
\v 19 Eḡeꞌa zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa haḡai sauꞌa haḡaeꞌetene, e rozeꞌohe zu sinasinazeꞌohe. Eꞌanoꞌo haḡai sauꞌa mene haḡaifine inaroꞌi zu ḡihuroꞌi.  
\v 20 Ḡianoꞌi. E ibiheta babaḡano edanadu toketokereꞌohe. Iniuꞌa eḡe ago egadu ibiheta eꞌe vavaꞌine, e diuḡadu ani teite ogaꞌuma zu aniꞌe eḡe teite ogaꞌuma.  
\v 21 Sauꞌa ḡauḡa raharahaneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe kini ehoro iḡuꞌano eḡe teite ehorogaꞌe idaḡa rae reꞌuma. Aꞌe eḡeꞌa sauꞌa ḡauḡa raharahaniroteꞌe enogano, e eḡe Mama kini ehoro iḡuꞌano ani teite ehoriroteꞌe teigiꞌuma.  
\v 22 Iniu teḡaḡota roꞌidene, Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ekalesia mazao ḡoereꞌeteꞌe egoꞌi.'” \fig Iesuꞌa ibihetao toketokereꞌohe|src="cn02107B.tif" size="col" ref="3:20" \fig*   
\c 4  
\s1 Adure Kuruḡa  
\p
\v 1 Eꞌe enogano eḡeꞌa horonirotene, adureo ibiheta ꞌahoga vavaꞌogaꞌe eꞌe. Ebu ibite eḡeꞌa igiroteꞌe agoḡa, bigoro agoḡa teigiroteꞌeꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, “ꞋAhi eroi. ꞌAhi enogano naginiꞌa fureru huniteꞌe eḡeꞌa ihoꞌiꞌuma.”  
\v 2 Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ḡarihe fase eḡe ragatiro ebu e adureo kini ehoro iḡuꞌa ꞌahoga horoniro. Eꞌe rana vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ehore radiro.  
\v 3 Eꞌe rana ehore radiuꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa iraḡaꞌe agaḡa ꞌuruḡa zu kanaḡaniꞌa agararo. Agaḡa aꞌe hadi ꞌuruḡa naeḡa boro niḡa iasipa zu hadi kanaḡa naeḡa boro niḡa sadio heuḡa. Ebu kini ehoro iḡuꞌaꞌe mezoneꞌa hadi ḡabodoraḡa naeḡa boro niḡa samaragi teige varahuniro.  
\v 4 Ebu kini ehoro iḡuꞌa aꞌe kini ehoro iḡuꞌa ꞌahoga niduꞌa 24ꞌa varahe huniro, ebu ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa 24ꞌa eꞌe ehoro iḡuꞌano ehore radiro. Zeꞌe dabua ꞌuruḡa haḡairo zu vadinizeo golo hina haḡairoteꞌe kini vadini adiriḡa ridiro.  
\v 5 Kini ehoro iḡuꞌa eꞌeanoꞌo agaru vazahe ovairo ebu viriꞌa fuꞌuradu gudaro. Kini ehoro iḡuꞌa eꞌe zamao ihure mozareḡa fuꞌo aheu fareꞌa duhuru agaru radiro. Ihure aꞌe Badiꞌa viga fuꞌo aheu fare.  
\v 6 Kini ehoro iḡuꞌa eꞌe zamaoꞌe galasi hina haḡairoteꞌe davaraḡa heuḡa eꞌe. Aꞌe naeḡa boro hadiḡa niḡa kirisita teige deheḡa bagaḡa.  
\p Kini ehoro iḡuꞌa eꞌe varahoga ḡonaga ḡazaḡano ḡaboga ḡauḡa ḡazaḡaꞌe eꞌe. Zeꞌe zama zu ḡaruni moneo ubuma daꞌodaꞌoroga.  
\v 7 Ḡaboga ḡauḡa ibiꞌaꞌe laioni heuḡa, aheuḡaꞌe boromakau ubuga ohozeḡa heuḡa, uḡiduḡaꞌe vaze iraḡa heuḡa, ebu ḡazaḡaꞌe rafiuꞌeteꞌe ugabadaḡa heuḡa.  
\v 8 Ḡaboga ḡauḡa ḡazaḡa tibatibaꞌe isaze fuꞌo tiba farezeta. Isaze zamaḡa zu enoga niduꞌaꞌe ubuma daꞌodaꞌoroga. Madai zu ohere ze ꞌahige ḡoeroga mene hune riꞌiꞌohe,  
\q1 “Zaḡoḡa, zaḡoḡa, zaḡoḡa!  
\q1 Zuhiꞌa Boro Badiꞌa Gigiꞌa hune!  
\q2 Ibite radiro, izidi radiuꞌohe, zu vesuꞌu ariteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa.”   
\m
\v 9 Badiꞌaꞌe radiu tuḡutuḡu, zu kini ehoro iḡuꞌano ehore radiuꞌohe. Ḡaboga ḡauḡaniꞌa ani ni mae ḡihineꞌohe, zu gubaneꞌohe, zu ani mazao manoḡa tauḡi rae raꞌohe.  
\v 10 Ze ꞌouge haḡaeꞌetene, ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa 24ꞌa kini ehoro iḡuꞌano ehoreꞌeteꞌe zu radiu tuḡutuḡeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa zamao ḡuḡuradu kurauꞌohe. Ebu ze vadinize rana ridiroteꞌe kini vadini adiriḡa mae vaḡinadu kini ehoro iḡuꞌa eꞌe zamao mae tiꞌohe, ebu ꞌahige rae raꞌohe,   
\q1
\v 11 “Emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Badiꞌa!  
\q2 Vazeꞌa niḡo mae ḡihinoga, gubaꞌoga zu gigiꞌaḡo nigunogaꞌe duduḡa hune,  
\q1 mazaḡa ḡaeꞌa ḡau niduꞌa haḡairo.  
\q2 Ḡae urao zeꞌe ꞌize radiuꞌohe zu ḡabone meiro.”   
\c 5  
\s1 Soꞌa Ḡuaḡa ebu Mamoe Ubuga  
\p
\v 1 Ebu hena e kini ehoro iḡuꞌano ehore radiuꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌevore edaꞌeḡano soꞌa ḡuaḡa ꞌahoga horoniro. Eꞌe soꞌaḡa ḡuaḡa zamaḡano zu enoganoꞌe ḡoere mirihiro, ebu vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa mene vavaꞌoga veize kadaḡa niduꞌa fuꞌo aheu fare hina soꞌa ḡuaḡa kadane ꞌuiro.  
\v 2 Ebu e tuḡure viga gigiꞌaḡaniꞌa ago boro hina ꞌahige rae fureniroteꞌe horoniro, “Iniuꞌa soꞌa ḡuaḡa rana kadaḡa eꞌe mae vaḡinadu vavaꞌogaꞌe idaḡa?”  
\v 3 Rehano vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa soꞌa ḡuaḡa vavaꞌoga zu zamaḡa ḡianoga mene idararo. Adureo ga rahao ga raha ꞌuꞌuḡano zuni oꞌoꞌa hune.  
\v 4 Soꞌa ḡuaḡa eꞌe vavaꞌadu zamaḡa ḡianogaꞌe idaḡa raꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoga mene horoniro ꞌahine, e niau rudaro.  
\v 5 Rehano ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano ꞌahoganiꞌa ꞌahige rae ihiro, “Ago nianoꞌi. Ḡianoꞌi, Iuda urabo vazeḡa ꞌahoga, kini Davida mariga ḡihiꞌa hune, Laioni rae huneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa agire ḡauḡa raharahaniro. Aniꞌe kadaḡa fuꞌo aheu fare mae vaḡinadu soꞌa ḡuaḡa vavaꞌogaꞌe idaḡa.” \fig Soꞌa ḡuaḡa|src="HK00153B.TIF" size="col" ref="5:1-8" \fig*   
\p
\v 6 Ebu e mamoe ubuga ꞌahoga horoniro. Ani iraḡaꞌe vazeꞌa maroteꞌe heuḡa. Aniꞌe ḡaboga ḡauḡa ḡazaḡa zu ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa 24 nemaḡano, kini ehoro iḡuꞌa zama none nemao edau radiro. Ani araḡaꞌe fuꞌo aheu fare zu ubumaḡaꞌe fuꞌo aheu fare. Ubuma fuꞌo aheu fare aꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa haba niduꞌa tuḡuziroteꞌe viga fuꞌo aheu fare.  
\v 7 Mamoe ubuganiꞌa aradu kini ehoro iḡuꞌano ehoriroteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌevore edaꞌeḡanonoꞌo soꞌa ḡuaḡa eꞌe meiro.  
\v 8 Aniꞌa eꞌe meirotene, ḡaboga ḡauḡa ḡazaḡa zu ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa 24ꞌa mamoe ubuga zamao ḡuḡuriro. Zeḡe niduꞌaꞌe gabizeta ebu golo hina haḡairoteꞌe ḡoḡoreḡa oboniro. Ḡoḡore eꞌe zamaḡanoꞌe ꞌuvahu hohoḡaniꞌa iriꞌaviro. ꞌUvahu hohoḡaꞌe Badiꞌa mone azaḡa kuru.  
\v 9 Ebu ze bada iziga ꞌahige badahiro,  
\q1 “Ḡaꞌe soꞌa ḡuaḡa eꞌe mougaꞌe idaḡa,  
\q2 zu eꞌe rana kadaḡa mae vaḡinadu soꞌa ḡuaḡa eꞌe vavaꞌogaꞌe idaḡa.  
\q1 Mazaḡa vazeꞌa ḡamiro,  
\q2 ebu ḡa ḡae ru hina  
\q2 urabo niduꞌa, ḡoere nunu azaḡa niduꞌa, vaze nunu niduꞌa, zu habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo bohaze buziro, ebu ze tutuzadu Badiꞌa haro.   
\q1
\v 10 Ḡaeꞌa zeꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe azaḡano tutuziro, ebu Badiꞌa veize gaueꞌeteꞌe dibuꞌo azaḡano ohoziro.  
\q2 Eꞌanoꞌo zeꞌe rahao ḡau niduꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 11 Ebu hena e tuḡure viga ḡehaḡa horoniro zu agoze igiro. Ze kini ehoro iḡuꞌa zu ḡaboga ḡauḡaḡauḡa ebu ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa varahiro. Zeꞌe ufeta ḡehaḡa bagaḡa radu zeḡe niduꞌa meꞌodoga zuni mene idararo.  
\v 12 Zeꞌe ago boro hina ꞌahige badahiro,  
\q1 “Vazeꞌa maroteꞌe Mamoeḡa Ubugaꞌe  
\q1 gigiꞌaḡa, maꞌoraḡa, huhuzaḡa zu inaraḡa hune.  
\q1 Badiꞌaꞌa haḡairoteꞌe ḡauḡa niduꞌaꞌe ani gubaniꞌuma zu niḡa mae ḡihiniꞌuma zu niguniꞌuma!”   
\p
\v 13 Ebu hena adureo, rahao, raha ꞌuꞌuḡano zu davarao—habaꞌa niduꞌa zamaḡano Badiꞌaꞌa haḡairoteꞌe ḡauḡa niduꞌa ꞌahige badaheꞌeteꞌe igiro,  
\q1 “Kini ehoro iḡuꞌano ehoreꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa zu Mamoe Ubuga  
\q1 niguzihi, gubazihi, nize mae ḡihizihi, zu gigiꞌaze niguzihi,  
\q2 onamo tuḡutuḡu!”   
\m
\v 14 ꞌOugadu ḡaboga ḡauḡa ḡazaḡaniꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, “Amen!” Ebu ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa Badiꞌa zu Mamoe Ubuga mazao ḡuḡuradu kuraro.   
\c 6  
\s1 Kadaḡa Fuꞌo Tiba Fare mae Vaḡiniro  
\p
\v 1 Ebu hena e Mamoe Ubuganiꞌa kadaḡa fuꞌo aheu fare boꞌaḡano tiba mae vaḡiniroteꞌe horoniro. Ebu ḡaboga ḡauḡa ḡazaḡa boꞌaḡano ꞌahoganiꞌa viri guguḡa agoḡa heuḡa hina ꞌahige raꞌeteꞌe igiro, “Aroi!”  
\v 2 Ebu eḡeꞌa ehamarotene, hosi ꞌuruḡa ꞌahogaꞌe eꞌe. Eꞌe rana ehoriroteꞌe vazaḡaꞌe feva oboniro, ebu Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo kini vadini adiriḡa meiro. Aniꞌa onamadu agire azaḡa raharahaziro, ebu bare raharahazoga veize onamiro.   
\p
\v 3 Mamoe Ubuganiꞌa kadaḡa aheuḡa mae vaḡinirotene, e ḡaboga ḡauḡa aheuḡaniꞌa ꞌahige raꞌeteꞌe igiro, “Aroꞌi!”  
\v 4 ꞌOugirotene, hosi ꞌahoga kanaḡa bagaḡaniꞌa fureraro. Hosi eꞌe rana ehoriroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo inara zu benisi boro meiro. Eꞌe inaraḡaꞌe raha azaḡaniꞌa utite roꞌoretitoga veize raha ꞌadanoꞌo uniho manoḡa mae vaḡineꞌeteꞌe inaraḡa.   
\p
\v 5 Mamoe Ubuganiꞌa kadaḡa uḡiduḡa mae vaḡinirotene, e ḡaboga ḡauḡa uḡiduḡaniꞌa ꞌahige raꞌeteꞌe igiro, “Aroi!” Ebu e ehamarotene, hosi ḡuꞌa ꞌahogaꞌe eꞌe. Eꞌe rana ehoriroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ꞌevoꞌano ḡau ꞌahoga oboniro. Eꞌe ḡauḡaꞌe aduga ga ufiḡa udaheꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa.  
\v 6 Ebu e ḡaboga ḡauḡa ḡazaḡa nemaḡanonoꞌo ago ꞌahoga heuḡaniꞌa hosi eꞌe rana ehoriroteꞌe vazeḡa mazao ꞌahige raꞌeteꞌe igiro, “Ogomu ferezoꞌi. Mada tiba gauḡa naeḡa\f + \fr 6:6 \fqa denari tiba \f* hina vuidi kilo tiba daꞌo hoitoga idaraꞌuma, ebu mada tiba gauḡa naeḡa hina bali kilo uḡidu daꞌo hoitoga idaraꞌuma. Rehano olivi dehoroḡa zu vaini vuḡa ago sausaunoꞌi.” \fig Aduga ga ufiḡa udaheꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa|src="HK00156B.TIF" size="col" ref="6:5-6" \fig*   
\p
\v 7 Mamoe Ubuganiꞌa kadaḡa ḡazaḡaḡa mae vaḡinirotene, e ḡaboga ḡauḡa ḡazaḡaḡaniꞌa ꞌahige raꞌeteꞌe igiro, “Aroꞌi!”  
\v 8 Ebu eꞌa horonirotene, hosi boraḡa ḡabodoraḡa ꞌahogaꞌe eꞌe. Eꞌe rana ehoriroteꞌe vazeḡa niḡaꞌe Rune. Ebu rune azaḡa haba niḡa Hadesiꞌa Rune ḡaruna hegotinu. Zeꞌe haba niduꞌaonoꞌo haba ḡazaḡano rovonadu haba tiba zamaḡano radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zimiꞌeteꞌe inaraḡa Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo meiro. Ze benisi, zaga, ugi, ebu rahao butu agireḡa hina vaze zemogaꞌe idaḡa rae reiro.   
\p
\v 9 Mamoe Ubuganiꞌa kadaḡa fuꞌoḡa mae vaḡinirotene, e vaze nu vinezeꞌe dibuꞌo fataḡa ꞌuꞌuḡano radoga horoziro. Zeꞌe Badiꞌa ḡoere haramiroteꞌe uꞌano zu zeꞌa rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa uꞌano, vazeꞌa zimiroteꞌe azaḡa viga.  
\v 10 Ze agoze boro hina ꞌahige huaro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro Gigiꞌaḡa Hune, ḡaꞌe zaḡoḡa zu huga. Ḡa noꞌe madaḡano raha ꞌadao radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa kotaziꞌuma, zu emeꞌa rufe soroniroteꞌe uꞌano naeze baronoziniꞌuma? Eme mada faḡa nugu guhiꞌiꞌuma?”  
\v 11 Zeḡe niduꞌaꞌe Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo dabua ꞌuruḡa meiro. Ebu Badiꞌaꞌa ꞌahige rae ziro, “Mada tahiḡa bare ahirize ohonoꞌi, onamo vazeꞌa zae zimiroteꞌe teige, zae teite gauiroteꞌe tuḡure azaḡa ebu ekalesia nego nabudi nuꞌe zimiꞌuma. Eḡeꞌa runeo tuḡuziꞌuma rae ohotiroteꞌe azaḡa naba niduꞌa iriꞌavine, naeze baronoziniꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 12 E Mamoe Ubuganiꞌa kadaḡa fuꞌo tiba fareḡa mae vaḡiniroteꞌe horoniro. Eꞌe madaḡano rahaꞌa borofe hagariro, zu madaꞌa dabua baruḡa ḡuꞌa teige ḡutaro, ebu batoꞌa ru teige kanararo.  
\v 13 Adureo buzuvaꞌe zavara boroꞌa zaidanadu figi ireḡaonoꞌo figi maḡa gogoḡaniꞌa rururaroteꞌe teige, rahao rururaro.  
\v 14 Adureꞌe soꞌa aneꞌa bare ḡuauꞌeteꞌe teige dauḡiro. Maḡa niduꞌa zu ꞌumu niduꞌa iḡurizeonoꞌo mae vaḡiziro.   
\p
\v 15 ꞌOugirotene, rahao kini azaḡa, zuhiꞌa azaḡa, uti azaḡa boroboro, maꞌora azaḡa, inara borozeta azaḡa, tuḡure azaḡa, zu mene tuḡure azaḡaniꞌa hadi hoꞌogano zu maḡamaḡa vatavaḡa boꞌaḡano uꞌuraro.  
\v 16 Zeꞌe maḡa zu vatava mazao ꞌahige rae huaro, “Eme fikifadu kini ehoro iḡuꞌano ehoreꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa ubumaonoꞌo zu Mamoe Ubuga zama ḡugiꞌanonoꞌo eme mae ꞌuꞌuru toꞌi.  
\v 17 Badiꞌa zu Mamoe Ubuga zamazeꞌa ḡugizeꞌeteꞌe madaḡa boroꞌa ariro. Iniuꞌa zamaze ḡugionoꞌo ḡabodogaꞌe idaḡa reꞌuma? Oꞌoꞌa hune!”   
\c 7  
\s1 Isaraela Azaḡa 144,000 Imoriro  
\p
\v 1 Eꞌe enogano e tuḡure viga ḡazaḡaniꞌa raha genaḡa ḡazaḡano edauꞌenoga horoziro. Ze zavaraꞌa raha rana ga davara rana ga ireni ꞌahoga rana mene zaidanoga veize, zavara ḡazaḡa obonadu ꞌue radiro.  
\v 2 Ebu e tuḡure viga ꞌahoganiꞌa madaꞌa iteꞌeteꞌe moneonoꞌo ite feureꞌenoga horoniro. Aniꞌe ḡabode radiuꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa mazaonoꞌo imoro meiro. Ani haba zu davara sausauneꞌeteꞌe gigiꞌaḡa meiroteꞌe tuḡureḡa viga ḡazaḡa mazao agoḡa boro hina ꞌahige huau ziro,  
\v 3 “Haba ga davara ga ire ago sausaunoꞌi, onamo emeꞌa emeḡe Badiꞌa tuḡure azaḡa zehereze rana imoroziꞌuma.”  
\v 4 Ebu e iniu imoroziroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe nugu rae igiro. Aꞌe Isaraela azaḡa urabo niduꞌaonoꞌo vaze niduꞌa 144,000.  
\v 5 Urabo tibatibaonoꞌo imoroziroteꞌe azaḡa nabaḡaꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe:  
\li1 Iuda uraboonoꞌo 12,000,  
\li1 Rubena uraboonoꞌo 12,000,  
\li1 Gado uraboonoꞌo 12,000,   
\li1
\v 6 Asere uraboonoꞌo 12,000,  
\li1 Nafatali uraboonoꞌo 12,000,  
\li1 Manase uraboonoꞌo 12,000,   
\li1
\v 7 Simeona uraboonoꞌo 12,000,  
\li1 Levi uraboonoꞌo 12,000,  
\li1 Isakara uraboonoꞌo 12,000,   
\li1
\v 8 Zebulono uraboonoꞌo 12,000,  
\li1 Iosefa uraboonoꞌo 12,000,  
\li1 Beniamini uraboonoꞌo 12,000.   
\s1 Dabua ꞌUruḡa Vidaroteꞌe Azaḡa Ḡuḡuvaḡa  
\p
\v 9 Eꞌe enogano e vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa horoziro. Zeꞌe ufeta ḡehaḡa radu vazeni ꞌahoganiꞌa ze meꞌodogaꞌe mene idararo. Zeꞌe haba niduꞌaonoꞌo, urabo niduꞌaonoꞌo, vaze nunu niduꞌaonoꞌo, zu ḡoere nunu azaḡa niduꞌaonoꞌo ariro. Zeꞌe dabua ꞌuruḡa vidaro, zu ꞌevorezeo sigi rouḡa oboniro, ebu kini ehoro iḡuꞌa zamao zu Mamoe Ubuga zamao edau radiro.  
\v 10 Ebu zeꞌe ago boro hina ꞌahige huau reiro,  
\q1 “Kini ehoro iḡuꞌano ehoreꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, emeḡe Badiꞌa,  
\q1 zu Mamoe Ubuganiꞌa eme ḡabofeꞌohe!”   
\m
\v 11 Tuḡure viga niduꞌa kini ehoro iḡuꞌa zu ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu ḡaboga ḡauḡa ḡazaḡa edau varahiro. Ebu ze kini ehoro iḡuꞌa zamao ḡuḡuradu Badiꞌa mazao kuraro.  
\v 12 Tuḡure viga niduꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro,  
\q1 “Amen!  
\q1 Badiꞌaꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune zu huhuzaḡa, ebu gigiꞌaḡa zu inaraḡaꞌe boro hune.  
\q1 Eme ani ni mae ḡihinihi,  
\q1 ani mazao manoḡa tauḡi reihi,  
\q1 zu ani gubanihi, onamo tuḡutuḡu.  
\q1 Amen!”   
\p
\v 13 Ebu hena ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano ꞌahoganiꞌa ꞌahige ḡadihiro, “Dabua ꞌuruḡa vidaroteꞌe azaḡa ꞌahiꞌe iniu? Zeꞌe noumanoꞌo areha?”  
\v 14 Ebu e ꞌahige naenaeniro, “Vaze boro, aꞌe ḡae edeḡa.” Ebu aniꞌa ꞌahige ihiro, “ꞌAhi azaḡaꞌe aduga boro zamaḡano zamaze obone giganiroteꞌe azaḡa. Zeꞌe Mamoe Ubuga ruḡa zamaḡano dabuaze vuzuꞌadu dabuazeꞌa ꞌuraro.  
\v 15 Eꞌe uꞌano,  
\q1 zeꞌe Kini Badiꞌa ehoro iḡuꞌa zamao edauꞌohe,  
\q2 ebu madai zu ohereo ane kuru neḡano ane veize gaueꞌohe.  
\q1 Ebu kini ehoro iḡuꞌano ehoreꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡaniꞌa taruhazi biriꞌuma.   
\q1
\v 16 Zeꞌe mene bare viniziꞌuma,  
\q2 mene bare irine moꞌoziꞌuma.  
\q1 Madaꞌa ze mene iri gigiziꞌuma,  
\q2 gigiꞌa bagaḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa ze mene iriꞌuma.   
\q1
\v 17 Kini ehoro iḡuꞌa nemaḡano radiuꞌeteꞌe Mamoeḡa Ubugaꞌe mamoe taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa teige ze taufiꞌuma,  
\q2 ebu aniꞌa ze tutuzadu ḡabone ziniꞌeteꞌe iduḡa vuḡa vaḡe onamiꞌuma.  
\q1 Ebu Badiꞌaꞌa ubumazeonoꞌo nize vuḡa niduꞌa zauhoziniꞌuma.”   
\c 8  
\s1 Kadaḡa Fuꞌo Aheu Fareḡa mae Vaḡiniro  
\p
\v 1 Mamoe Ubuganiꞌa kadaḡa fuꞌo aheu fareḡa mae vaḡinirotene, adureꞌe mada tahiḡa sifu radiro.  
\v 2 Ebu e Badiꞌa zamao edauꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa viga fuꞌo aheu fare horoziro. Zeḡe niduꞌa Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo bigoro meiro.   
\p
\v 3 Ebu tuḡure viga ꞌahoganiꞌa dibuꞌo fataḡa uhiḡano aradu edaro. Aniꞌe ꞌuvahu hohoḡa hufiꞌeteꞌe ḡoḡoreḡa golo hina haḡairoteꞌe obone radiro. Aniꞌe tuḡure viga ꞌahoga mazaonoꞌo ꞌuvahu hohoḡa boro bagaḡa meiro. Ebu ꞌuvahu hohoḡa eꞌe Badiꞌa mone azaḡa niduꞌa kuruze teite kini ehoro iḡuꞌa zamao golo hina haḡairoteꞌe dibuꞌoḡa fataḡa rana dibuꞌoharo.  
\v 4 Ebu tuḡure viganiꞌa ꞌuvahu hohoḡa hufirotene, ḡisiḡaniꞌa Badiꞌa mone azaḡa kuruze teite tiburu ani ꞌevoreonoꞌo Badiꞌa vaḡe itiro.  
\v 5 Ebu hena tuḡure viganiꞌa ꞌuvahu hohoḡa hufiꞌeteꞌe ḡoḡoreḡa madu dibuꞌo fataḡanonoꞌo ire roga hina iriꞌavoniro, ebu raha rana ḡuzuni feuniro. ꞌOugirotene, viriꞌa agaru vazahiro, zu ḡihau gudaro, ebu fuꞌuriro, zu rahaꞌa hagariro.   
\s1 Bigoro Fuꞌo Aheu Fare  
\p
\v 6 Ebu hena tuḡure viga fuꞌo aheu fareꞌa bigoro fuꞌo aheu fare madu hodoga veize ruhibiro.   
\p
\v 7 Tuḡure viga ibiꞌaḡaniꞌa bigoroḡa hudirotene, ḡoze hatuꞌaḡa zu ire rogaꞌe ru teite tiburanadu rahao rururaro. Ebu raha niduꞌaonoꞌo uḡide rovonadu tiba mone rovonoga rahaḡaꞌe hufi haoniro. Ebu ire niduꞌaonoꞌo uḡide rovonadu tiba mone rovonoga ireḡa hufi haoniro, zu imi ḡabodoraḡa eꞌe rahaḡa niduꞌa hufi haoniro.   
\p
\v 8 Tuḡure viga aheuḡaniꞌa bigoroḡa hudirotene, maḡa boro ire rogaꞌa iriꞌeteꞌe teigeꞌetaꞌaꞌe davarao mae feuniro. Ebu davara niduꞌaonoꞌo davara uḡide rovonadu tiba mone rovonoga davaraḡaꞌe ru reiro.  
\v 9 Davarao ḡaboga ḡauḡa niduꞌaonoꞌo uḡide rovonadu tiba mone ḡaboga ḡauḡaꞌe rudaro. Ebu ḡasi boro niduꞌaonoꞌo uḡide rovonadu tiba mone rovonoga ḡasiḡaꞌe faharo.   
\p
\v 10 Tuḡure viga uḡiduḡaniꞌa bigoroḡa hudirotene, buzuva ꞌahoga boro bagaḡaniꞌa ihure teige duhuru agaruꞌenaꞌa, adureonoꞌo rururaro. Aꞌe vu boro niduꞌaonoꞌo uḡide rovonadu tiba mone rovonoga vuḡa boro rana zu idu vuḡa rana rururaro.  
\v 11 Buzuva eꞌe niḡaꞌe Agiꞌa. Eꞌanoꞌo aniꞌa vu boro niduꞌaonoꞌo uḡide rovonadu tiba mone rovonoga vuḡa boroboro aginiro. Ebu agitaroteꞌe vuḡa uꞌano, vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa eꞌe gagadu rudau ḡouriro.   
\p
\v 12 Tuḡure viga ḡazaḡaḡaniꞌa bigoroḡa hudirotene, mada nidugaonoꞌo uḡide rovonadu tiba mone madaḡaꞌe sausauniro. Ebu bato nidugaonoꞌo uḡide rovonadu tiba mone rovonogaꞌe sausauniro, zu buzuva niduꞌaonoꞌo uḡide rovonadu tiba mone rovonoga buzuvaḡaꞌe sausauniro. ꞌOugadu zeḡe agaḡa niduꞌaonoꞌo uḡide rovonadu tiba mone rovonoga agaḡaniꞌa dauḡiro. Eꞌanoꞌo madai agaḡa niduꞌaonoꞌo uḡide rovonadu tiba mone rovonoga agaḡaniꞌa dauḡiro, ebu ohere agaḡa niduꞌaonoꞌo uḡide rovonadu tiba mone rovonoga agaḡaniꞌa dauḡiro.   
\p
\v 13 Ebu hena eꞌa ehamaro zu igirotene, ugabada tibaniꞌa adure nemaḡano rafiuꞌenaꞌa, agoḡa boro hina ꞌahige rae reiro, “Aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Rahao radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa aduga boro hidiꞌuma, mazaḡa tuḡure viga uḡiduꞌa bigoroze nariga hudiꞌohe ebu ze aduga boro hidiꞌuma!”   
\c 9  
\p
\v 1 Tuḡure viga fuꞌoḡaniꞌa bigoroḡa hudirotene, e adureonoꞌo rahao rururaroteꞌe buzuvaḡa ꞌahoga horoniro. Eꞌe buzuvaḡaniꞌa iniuonoꞌo idu vo hune\f + \fr 9:1 \fqa Abisi \f* ibiḡa vavaꞌeꞌeteꞌe kiḡa meiro.  
\v 2 Buzuva eꞌeꞌa idu vo hune eꞌe vavaꞌirotene, eꞌeanoꞌo ḡisi boroꞌa ite buaro. Aꞌe ire roga mozareḡanonoꞌo buauꞌeteꞌe ḡisiḡa teigiro. Eꞌanoꞌo idu eꞌeanoꞌo ḡisi uꞌano, mada zu adureꞌa uzaboraro.  
\v 3 Ebu hena ḡisi eꞌeanoꞌo fihoreꞌa rahao bua ariro, ebu zeꞌe Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo rahao asiasi inaraḡa heuḡa inara meiro.  
\v 4 Badiꞌaꞌa ꞌahige rae ziro, “Raha veḡa ga rahao ḡuhureꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa ga ire niduꞌa ago sausaunoꞌi, rehano Badiꞌa imoro zehereze rana oꞌoꞌa azaḡa daꞌo sausauzoꞌi.”  
\v 5 Zeꞌe vaze ꞌuguḡa zimiꞌeteꞌe inaraḡaꞌe mene meiro, rehano bato fuꞌo zamaḡano aduga zenogaꞌe idaḡa rae reiro. Zeꞌa aduga zenadu eꞌe azaḡaꞌe gigiꞌa boro hidiro. Zeḡe gigiꞌaꞌe asiasiꞌa vaze asize gigizeꞌeteꞌe teigiro.  
\v 6 Eꞌe madaḡano gigiꞌa hidiroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa rune ibiḡa vaḡiꞌuma, rehano mene horoniꞌuma. Zeꞌe rudanoga urate huniꞌuma, rehano runeꞌa ze mazaonoꞌo feraꞌuma.   
\p
\v 7 Fihore irazeꞌe uti veize ruhibiroteꞌe hosiḡa heuḡa. Vadinizeo golo hina haḡairoteꞌe kini vadini adiriḡa heuḡa ridiro, ebu ubumazeꞌe vaze ubuma heuḡa.  
\v 8 Vadinize iguḡaꞌe roḡae vadini iguḡa heuḡa, zu ḡononezeꞌe laioni ḡonone heuḡa.  
\v 9 Zeꞌe uꞌuni bireꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa vidaro. Aꞌe auri hina haḡairoteꞌe ḡauḡa heuḡa. Isaze ḡokeḡaꞌe hosi ḡehaḡaniꞌa hasiseꞌeteꞌe kiuḡaniꞌa uti onameꞌenaꞌa, borofe ḡokereꞌeteꞌe heuḡa.  
\v 10 Avaze zu gohezeꞌe asiasi heuḡa. Avazeꞌe bato fuꞌo vaze sausauzeꞌeteꞌe inaraḡazeta.  
\v 11 Ze idu vo huneonoꞌo bua eriroteꞌe tuḡureḡa vigaꞌe zeḡe kini rae reiro. Kini niḡaꞌe Heberu ḡoeꞌano Abadoni,\f + \fr 9:11 \ft Hugaꞌe Ruizoga. \f* u Giriki ḡoeꞌanoꞌe Apoliona.\f + \fr 9:11 \ft Hugaꞌe Ruizeꞌeteꞌe Vazeḡa. \f*   
\p
\v 12 Aduga boro ibiꞌaꞌe hauḡiro. Rehano aduga boro aheuḡa ꞌize areꞌohe. \fig Hosi ḡehaḡaniꞌa hasiseꞌeteꞌe kiuḡa|src="HK00191B.TIF" size="col" ref="9:9" \fig*   
\p
\v 13 Tuḡure viga fuꞌo tiba fareḡaniꞌa bigoroḡa hudirotene, e Badiꞌa zamao golo hina haḡairoteꞌe dibuꞌo fataḡa genaḡa araḡa ḡazaḡaonoꞌo ago ꞌahoga igiro.  
\v 14 Ago eꞌeꞌa tuḡure viga fuꞌo tiba fareḡa bigoroḡeta ꞌahige rae niro, “Euferate vuḡa boro zamaḡano batuziroteꞌe tuḡureḡa viga ḡazaḡa fuhiꞌe ahetoꞌi.”  
\v 15 Eꞌanoꞌo tuḡure viga ḡazaḡa fuhiꞌe ahetiro. Zeꞌe vaze niduꞌaonoꞌo uḡide rovozadu tiba mone rovonoga azaḡa zimifine, eꞌe madaḡa, eꞌe batoḡa zu eꞌe muriḡa veize Badiꞌaꞌa ruhibiro.  
\v 16 E tuḡure viga ḡazaḡa mone uti azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe nugu rae igiro. Zeꞌe hosi rana ehoradu utiteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, ebu zeḡe niduꞌaꞌe 200 milioni.  
\v 17 E ahiri raꞌaga iḡunaḡano hosi ḡehaḡa zu hosi eꞌe rana ehoreꞌeteꞌe azaḡa horoziro. Ze uꞌunize bireꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa vidaro. Uꞌunize bireꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡaꞌe ire roga heuḡa kanaḡa, zu buluḡa, zu ḡau ꞌahoga niḡa sulifu\f + \fr 9:17 \ft Sulifuꞌe ire roga ufeta gigiꞌaḡano haḡaifine tiꞌohe ebu ufeta ḡezauꞌohe. \f* heuḡa boraḡa. Hosi vadiniꞌe laioni vadiga heuḡa, ebu hebezeonoꞌo ire roga, ḡisi zu sulifuꞌa buaro.  
\v 18 Hosi hebezeonoꞌo buaroteꞌe ire roga, ḡisi zu sulifu—aduga uḡidu eꞌe ꞌahine, vaze niduꞌaonoꞌo uḡide rovozadu tiba mone rovonoga azaḡaꞌe rudaro.  
\v 19 Hosi hebezeo zu avazeo inarazeta. Avazeꞌe mohe heuḡa, ebu avazeoꞌe vadinizeta. Ze avazeo vadinize nu hina vaze sausauziro.   
\p
\v 20 Rehano aduga ꞌuguḡanonoꞌo mene rudaroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe ꞌevoreze hina haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡanonoꞌo mene ḡihuriro. Zeꞌe vine sauꞌa zu ḡuriro badiꞌaḡa mazao kuranoga mene modiro. Ḡuriro badiꞌaḡaꞌe golo, siliva, kopa, hadi zu ire hina haḡadu ze ehamanoga, abitoga zu ragavogaꞌe mene idaḡa. Rehano vazeꞌa zeḡe mazao kuranogaꞌe mene modiro.  
\v 21 Zuni ze vaze zemoga, murava haḡaiḡa, daro fuꞌa ebu ḡonoreonoꞌo mene ḡihuriro.   
\c 10  
\s1 Tuḡure Viga ebu Soꞌa Ḡuaḡa Komeḡa  
\p
\v 1 Ebu hena e tuḡure viga gigiꞌa ꞌahoga adureonoꞌo ovaoga horoniro. Ḡozeꞌa ani varahiro ebu vadiga ranaꞌe mezoneḡeta. Ani ubumaꞌe mada heuḡa, ebu ani odaꞌe ire roga gadoḡa heuḡa.  
\v 2 Aniꞌe ꞌevoꞌano soꞌa ḡuaḡa komeḡa vavaꞌoga obone radiro. Edaꞌe odaḡaꞌe davara rana edaro, ebu kauri odaḡaꞌe raha rana edaro.  
\v 3 Ebu laioniꞌa gudauꞌeteꞌe teige ago boro hina ḡihau huaro. Aniꞌa huarotene, viri fuꞌo aheu fareꞌa gudauꞌenaꞌa ḡoeriro.  
\v 4 Viri fuꞌo aheu fareꞌa gudau ḡoerirotene, e nariga ḡoere eꞌe mirihe fariro. Rehano e adureonoꞌo ago ꞌahoganiꞌa ꞌahige rae reiroteꞌe igiro, “Viri fuꞌo aheu fareꞌa reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe ꞌuꞌuru toꞌi. Aꞌe ago mirihoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 5 Ebu hena eḡeꞌa horoniroteꞌe tuḡureḡa viga, davara rana zu raha rana edau radiuꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa viganiꞌa edaꞌe ꞌevoꞌa adure ḡoha mae ḡihiniro.  
\v 6 Ebu aniꞌa radiu tuḡutuḡu Badiꞌaḡa, adure zu adureo ḡau niduꞌa, raha zu rahao ḡau niduꞌa, ebu davara zu davarao ḡau niduꞌa haḡairoteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa niḡano ꞌahige ḡoere rinede tiro, “Badiꞌaꞌa toganiroteꞌe madaḡa mene sasiꞌuma.  
\v 7 Tuḡure viga fuꞌo aheu fareḡaniꞌa bigoroḡa huditeꞌe madaḡano, Badiꞌaꞌa toganiroteꞌe ḡauḡa ꞌuꞌuru tiroteꞌeꞌa hudaꞌuma. Aꞌe ane tuḡure azaḡa, peroveta azaḡa ihoziroteꞌe idunaḡano hudaꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 8 Ebu hena adureonoꞌo eꞌa igiroteꞌe agoḡaniꞌa bare ꞌahige ḡorehiro, “Ḡa onamadu davara rana zu raha rana edauꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa viga ꞌevoꞌano soꞌa ḡuaḡa komeḡa vavaꞌoga moꞌi.”  
\v 9 Eꞌanoꞌo e tuḡure viga eꞌe vaḡe onamadu soꞌa ḡuaḡa komeḡa eꞌe enoga uminiro. Ebu tuḡure viganiꞌa ꞌahige ihiro, “ꞌAhi madu anoꞌi. Eꞌe aune, ḡae hebeoꞌe ꞌavore godaḡa teige iniga reꞌuma, rehano ḡae isioꞌe agiꞌa reꞌuma.”  
\v 10 Eꞌa tuḡure viga eꞌe ꞌevoꞌanonoꞌo soꞌa ḡuaḡa komeḡa madu aro. Aꞌe hebeheo ꞌavore godaḡa teige iniga, rehano eꞌe aroteꞌe enoganoꞌe isiheo agihiro.  
\v 11 Ebu hena ꞌahige ihiro, “Ḡaꞌa vaze nunu, habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa, ḡoere nunu azaḡa zu kini nunu moneo Badiꞌa ḡoere bare rae furene huniꞌuma.”   
\c 11  
\s1 Badiꞌa Ḡoere rae Fureniroteꞌe Azaḡa Aheu  
\p
\v 1 Iniuꞌa tuḡu teige faḡa zu rafaḡa udaheꞌeteꞌe somoriḡa ꞌahoga iniro, ebu ꞌahige ihiro, “Ḡa onamadu Badiꞌa kuru neḡa zu dibuꞌo fataḡa faḡa ebu rafaḡa nuguꞌe udahoꞌi, ebu vaze niduꞌa nuguꞌa eꞌea kurauꞌeteꞌe meꞌodoꞌi.  
\v 2 Rehano kuru neḡa enoga habaꞌaꞌe ago zamaroꞌi ebu ago udahoꞌi, mazaḡa aꞌe Iuda mene azaḡa ziniro. Zeꞌe bato 42 zamaḡano ne boro zaḡoḡa, Ierusalema edau ḡahiniꞌuma.  
\v 3 Ebu eḡeꞌa eḡe ḡoere rae fureneꞌeteꞌe azaḡa aheu inara ziniꞌuma. Ze zamaze aduga rae ihozifine dabua ḡuꞌa vidanadu mada 1,260 zamaḡano eḡe ḡoere rae fureniꞌuma.”  
\v 4 Zeꞌe raha ꞌadi Zuhiꞌaḡa Boro zamao edauꞌeteꞌe olivi ireḡa aheu ebu ihure odaḡa aheu rae idaziro.  
\v 5 Iniuꞌa ze sausauzihi rae reine, hebezeonoꞌo ire rogaꞌa buanadu agireze ruiziꞌuma. Iniuꞌa ze zimihi rae raꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ꞌouge mau runiꞌuma.  
\v 6 Ze zeḡeꞌa Badiꞌa ḡoere rae fureneꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano iruguꞌa mene ruꞌanoga veize adure ꞌueꞌeteꞌe inaraḡa meiro. Ebu ze vu ruo ḡihuneꞌeteꞌe inaraḡa meiro, zu ze urateꞌeteꞌe madaḡa niduꞌa zamaḡano raha ꞌahi aduga nunu hina sausauneꞌeteꞌe inaraḡa meiro. \fig Kuru neḡa|src="WA04003b.tif" size="col" ref="11:1" \fig*   
\p
\v 7 Zeḡe aheuꞌa Badiꞌa ḡoere rae furene hauḡine, idu vo huneonoꞌo butu agireḡaniꞌa bua eradu ze utitoziꞌuma ebu ze raharahazadu zimiꞌuma.  
\v 8 Ebu zeḡe rune ahiꞌaꞌe zeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro satauroniroteꞌe habaꞌa, ne boro ḡihiꞌaḡa ibiḡano mode tauḡiꞌuma. Ne boro aꞌe Sodoma zu Izipi rae idaniꞌuma.  
\v 9 Vaze nunu niduꞌa, urabo niduꞌa, ḡoere nunu azaḡa niduꞌa, ebu habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa mada uḡidu ḡahaꞌeta zamaḡano rune ahirize muririꞌuma, ebu rune ahirize guroga hezahohaꞌuma.  
\v 10 Rahao radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa rune ahirize uꞌano matuꞌiꞌuma, zu mui haḡaiꞌuma, ebu ḡahunone ḡahugotitiꞌuma. Mazaḡa peroveta azaḡa aheu eꞌeꞌa rahao radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa gigiꞌa boro ziniro.   
\p
\v 11 Rehano mada uḡidu ḡahaꞌeta enogano, Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo ḡabozeꞌeteꞌe irineḡaniꞌa buanadu rune ahirize zamaḡano diuḡiro. ꞌOugadu ze odaze hina edaro ebu ze muririroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ufeta rihau ḡouriro.  
\v 12 Ebu ze adureonoꞌo ago boro ꞌahoganiꞌa ꞌahige ziꞌeteꞌe igiro, “ꞋAhi eroꞌi.” ꞌOugadu ze ḡoze hina adure ḡoha itiro, u zeḡe agire azaḡaꞌe eꞌe muririro.  
\v 13 Eꞌe madaḡano, rahaꞌa borofe hagariro, ebu ne boro eꞌe zamaḡano ne niduꞌaonoꞌo gaubananao rovonadu tiba mone rovonoga neḡa niduꞌaꞌe higaro. Rahaꞌa hagariro ꞌahine, vaze niduꞌa 7,000ꞌa rudaro. Ebu mene rudaroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe rihau rudaro zu adureo Badiꞌa niḡa mae ḡihiniro.   
\p
\v 14 Aduga boro aheuḡaꞌe hauḡiro, rehano uḡiduḡaꞌe nariga areꞌohe.   
\s1 Bigoro Fuꞌo Aheu Fareḡa  
\p
\v 15 Tuḡure viga fuꞌo aheu fareḡaniꞌa bigoroḡa hudirotene, adureo ago boroꞌa gudanadu ꞌahige rae reiro,  
\q1 “Emeḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro Badiꞌa zu aniꞌa ohotiroteꞌe vazeḡa, Kerisoꞌa raha niduꞌa ibitoziꞌuma.  
\q2 Ebu Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌuma, onamo radiu tuḡutuḡu.”   
\m
\v 16 Ebu Badiꞌa zamao kini ehoro iḡuꞌano ehoreꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa 24ꞌa Badiꞌa mazao ḡuḡuradu kuraro.  
\v 17 Ze ꞌahige rae reiro,  
\q1 “Zuhiꞌa Boro Badiꞌa Gigiꞌaḡa,  
\q2 ḡaꞌe izidi radiuꞌeteꞌe zu ibite radiroteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa.  
\q1 Eme ḡae mazao manoḡa tauḡi raꞌohe,  
\q2 mazaḡa ḡaeꞌa gigiꞌa boro hune madu  
\q2 ḡau niduꞌa zuhiꞌazoga ḡadahiro.   
\q1
\v 18 Habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡaniꞌa ḡae mazao maḡuniro,  
\q2 rehano ḡae zama ḡugiꞌe zeḡe mazao fureniro.  
\q1 Rune azaḡa kotaziteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa feuriro.  
\q2 Ḡae tuḡure azaḡa, peroveta azaḡa, ḡae mone azaḡa, ebu  
\q2 iniu nize boro ga nize komeꞌa, ḡae gubaꞌeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mazao  
\q2 naeḡa manoḡa ziniteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa feuriro.  
\q1 Raha niduꞌa ruineꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ruiziteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa feuriro.”   
\p
\v 19 Ebu hena adureo Badiꞌa kuru neḡa vavaꞌiro, ebu ane kuru neḡa zamaḡano ane ḡoitore ḡoeꞌa tiroteꞌe mauḡaḡa horoniro. Eꞌe madaḡano vazahiro, borofe gudaro, viriꞌa fuꞌuriro, rahaꞌa hagariro, ebu ḡoze hatuꞌaḡaniꞌa borofe buaro.   
\c 12  
\s1 Roḡae Zu Isona Horeḡa  
\p
\v 1 Ebu hena haḡai nu badeḡa boro ꞌahoganiꞌa adureo fureraro. Roḡae ꞌahoganiꞌa madaꞌe dabua teige vidaro, ebu batoꞌe ani oda ꞌuꞌuḡano zu vadiga rana kini vadini adiriḡa ridiro. Ane kini vadini adiriḡaꞌe buzuva gaubanana aheu fareḡeta.  
\v 2 Aniꞌe ahiꞌeta, ebu ene nariga fureneꞌeteꞌe uꞌano gigiꞌa madu ḡihau ḡaniḡanaro.  
\v 3 Ebu hena haḡai nu badeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa adureo fureraro. Aꞌe isona horeḡa kanaḡa. Vadiga niduꞌaꞌe fuꞌo aheu fare zu araḡa niduꞌaꞌe gaubanana. Vadigano kini vadini adiriḡa fuꞌo aheu fare vidaro.  
\v 4 Ani avaḡaniꞌa adureo buzuvaḡa niduꞌaonoꞌo uḡide rovonadu tiba mone rovonoga buzuvaḡaꞌe fodadu rahao feuniro. Ebu isona horeḡaniꞌa roḡae eꞌe zamao edaro, mazaḡa roḡae eꞌeꞌa nariga ene fureniꞌuma ꞌahine, ene fureneꞌeteꞌe madaḡa huneo isona horeḡaniꞌa eneḡa atihi rae reiro.  
\v 5 Ebu roḡae ꞌai ubuga ꞌahoga fureniro. Ubugaꞌe auri somoriḡa riḡa hina haba niduꞌa zuhiꞌaziteꞌe vazeḡa. Rehano Badiꞌaꞌa ene guraḡa aꞌe mae vaḡinadu aniꞌa Badiꞌa zu Badiꞌa kini ehoro iḡuꞌa ḡoha itiro.  
\v 6 Ebu roḡae eꞌeꞌa haba bohaꞌa ferau onamiro. Deꞌea mada 1,260 zamaḡano vazeꞌa ani taufoga veize Badiꞌaꞌa haba ꞌahoga ruhibiro.   
\p
\v 7 Ebu hena adureo utiꞌa fureraro. Tuḡure viga ḡihiꞌaḡa, niḡa Mikaela zu ane tuḡure vigaviganiꞌa isona horeḡa teite utitiro. Isona horeḡa zu ane tuḡure vigaviganiꞌa zuni zeḡe teite utitiro.  
\v 8 Rehano Mikaela zu ane tuḡure vigaviganiꞌa isona horeḡa zu ane tuḡure vigaviga raharahazadu habaze adureoꞌe dauḡiro.  
\v 9 Eꞌanoꞌo isona horeḡaꞌe adureonoꞌo mae feune buniro. Aniꞌe ibite huneonoꞌo radiu onainuteꞌe moheḡa, ebu niḡaꞌe Diabolo ga Satani rae huneꞌohe. Aniꞌe raha azaḡa niduꞌa soꞌozadu veꞌoze ibitoziꞌohe. Ani rahao mae feuniro zu ane tuḡure vigaviga zuni ane teite mae feuziro. \fig Roḡae ebu isona horeḡa|src="67_Rev12:1,3_Woman& Dragon.tif" size="col" ref="12:1-4" \fig*   
\p
\v 10 Ebu hena e adureo ago boro ꞌahoganiꞌa ꞌahige raꞌeteꞌe igiro,  
\q1 “Izidi Badiꞌaꞌa ane mone azaḡa ḡabozeha.  
\q1 Aniꞌa ane inaraḡa zu aniꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe ihozeha.  
\q1 Aniꞌa ohoniroteꞌe vazeḡa, Kerisoꞌa gigiꞌaḡa ihozeha.  
\q1 Sauꞌa ḡauḡaniꞌa emeḡe nego nabudi veꞌoḡa rae agiroziro,  
\q2 ebu ohere zu madaio Badiꞌa zamao zeꞌe sauꞌa rae agiroziro.  
\q2 Rehano sauꞌa ḡauḡaꞌe mae feune buneha.   
\q1
\v 11 Ebu emeḡe nego nabudiꞌa Mamoe Ubuga ru uꞌano  
\q2 zu zeꞌa rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa uꞌano sauꞌa ḡauḡa raharahaneha.  
\q1 Zeḡeꞌa ḡaboneze mene zamariro, onamo rune hideha.   
\q1
\v 12 Eꞌanoꞌo adure zu adureo radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, matuꞌoꞌi!  
\q1 Rehano rahao zu davarao radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, za aduga boro hidiꞌuma,  
\q2 mazaḡa Diaboloꞌa zae vaḡe ovaeha.  
\q1 Aniꞌe zama ḡugi boroḡeta,  
\q2 mazaḡa ani edeḡa, ane madaꞌe futuꞌa.”   
\s1 Isona Horeḡaniꞌa Roḡae Mariga Utitozifine Ruhibiro  
\p
\v 13 Isona horeḡaniꞌe rahao mae feunirotaꞌaꞌe aneꞌa bare ederirotene, ubuga fureniroteꞌe roḡaeḡa eꞌe vaḡe uhine onamiro.  
\v 14 Rehano roḡae eꞌeꞌa haba bohaꞌano radoneḡa habaꞌa rafiu onamoga veize ugabada boro isaḡa aheuḡeta haro. Eꞌe habaꞌaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa ani veize ruhibiro, ebu ani deꞌea isona horeḡaonoꞌo vaḡinadu muri uḡidu ḡahaꞌeta zamaḡano vazeꞌa ani taufiro.  
\v 15 Ebu hena isona horeḡaniꞌa hebeꞌanonoꞌo vu boro hina roḡae eꞌe ḡaruga furure vanadu ani mae vaḡinihi reiro.  
\v 16 Rehano rahaꞌa ani dananiro. Rahaꞌa hebeꞌa vavaꞌadu isona horeḡaniꞌa hebeꞌanonoꞌo fururiroteꞌe vuḡa boro uniro.  
\v 17 Ebu hena isona horeḡaniꞌa roḡae eꞌe mazao maḡune rudanadu roḡae eꞌe mariga boꞌaḡano ḡabodeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa utitozenoga veize onamiro. Roḡae marigaꞌe Badiꞌa goro ḡoeꞌa egohauꞌeteꞌe zu Iesu moneo rae fureneꞌeteꞌe azaḡa.   
\p
\v 18 Ebu isona horeḡaniꞌa davara niꞌuriḡano edaro.   
\c 13  
\s1 Butu Agireḡa Ibiꞌa  
\p
\v 1 Ebu hena e butu agireḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa davaraonoꞌo bua areꞌeteꞌe horoniro. Ani araḡa niduꞌaꞌe gaubanana zu vadiga niduꞌaꞌe fuꞌo aheu fare. Araḡa tibatiba ranaꞌe kini vadini adiriḡa ridiro, zu vadini tibatiba ranaꞌe Badiꞌa rae sausauneꞌeteꞌe niḡa eꞌe.  
\v 2 Eꞌa horoniroteꞌe butu agireḡaꞌe butu agireḡa ꞌahoga, aꞌe leopadi heuḡa. Rehano ani odaꞌe bea oda heuḡa zu ani hebeꞌe laioni hebe heuḡa. Isona horeḡa eꞌeꞌa butu agireḡa mazao ane inara, ane kini ehoro iḡuꞌa zu gigiꞌaḡa ufeta boro haro.  
\v 3 Butu agireḡa vadini niduꞌa boꞌaḡano vadini tibaꞌe idiri boro madu horonogaꞌe nariga rudaro. Rehano idiriḡa aꞌe manoradu raha azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe zaguzagaro ebu butu agireḡa eꞌe hegotiro.  
\v 4 Vazevazeꞌa isona horeḡa eꞌe mazao kuraro, mazaḡa aniꞌa ane gigiꞌa butu agireḡa haro. Zeꞌe butu agireḡa eꞌe mazao zuni kuraro ebu ꞌahige rae reiro, “Butu agireḡa ꞌaha teigeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa inaraḡaꞌe oꞌoꞌa! Iniuꞌa ani utitohaꞌuma?” \fig Leopadi|src="HK003D.tif" size="col" ref="13:2" \fig*   
\p
\v 5 Badiꞌaꞌa butu agireḡaꞌe aneꞌa bare nigunoga zu Badiꞌa rae sausaunogaꞌe idaḡa rae reiro, ebu bato 42 zamaḡano ani vaze sausauzeꞌeteꞌe inaraḡa haro.  
\v 6 Ani hebeꞌa vavaꞌadu Badiꞌa rae sausauniro. Ebu Badiꞌa ni zu Badiꞌa radone habaꞌa ebu adureo radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa rae sausauziro.  
\v 7 Badiꞌaꞌa aniꞌe Badiꞌa mone azaḡa utitozenoga zu raharahazogaꞌe idaḡa rae reiro. Ebu urabo niduꞌa, vaze nunu niduꞌa, ḡoere nunu azaḡa niduꞌa, zu habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe inaraḡa haro.  
\v 8 Vazeꞌa maroteꞌe Mamoeḡa Ubuganiꞌa buka ꞌahogano ḡaboziteꞌe azaḡa nize mirihiro. Nizeꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa ꞌizema ḡau niduꞌa haḡaoganonoꞌo mirihiro. Raha azaḡa boꞌaḡano eꞌe bukaḡano Mamoe Ubuganiꞌa iniu nize mene mirihiroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe butu agireḡa eꞌe mazao kuraꞌuma.   
\p
\v 9 Iniu teḡaḡeta vazeḡaꞌe ꞌahi egoꞌi:   
\q1
\v 10 Badiꞌaꞌa vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa vaze ꞌahoga hube hune obone teadu ḡuꞌa neḡano ohonogaꞌe idaḡa rae reine,  
\q2 ani hube hune obone teadu ḡuꞌa neḡano diuḡiꞌuma.  
\q1 Badiꞌaꞌa vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa vaze ꞌahoga hube hune benisi hina manogaꞌe idaḡa rae reine,  
\q2 ani hube hune benisi hina manadu rudaꞌuma.  
\m Eꞌanoꞌo Badiꞌa mone azaḡaꞌe aduga zamaḡano zamaze obone gigane huniꞌuma, zu zeꞌa fieꞌetaꞌaꞌe mene hune modiꞌuma.   
\s1 Butu Agireḡa Aheuḡa  
\p
\v 11 Ebu hena e butu agireḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa rahaonoꞌo bua areꞌeteꞌe horoniro. Ani mamoe ubuga heuḡa araḡa aheu, rehano isona horeḡa teige ḡoeriro.  
\v 12 Aniꞌa butu agireḡa ibiꞌa inaraḡa niduꞌa hina butu agireḡa ibiꞌa veize gauiro. Ebu aniꞌa raha zu rahao radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe butu agireḡa ibiꞌa mazao kuranoga veize tutuziro. Butu agireḡa ibiꞌaꞌe ibite idiri boro madu nariga rudaro rehano, bare manoriro.  
\v 13 Butu agireḡa aheuḡaniꞌa haḡai nu badeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa haḡairo. Vaze niduꞌa murireꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano, aniꞌa adureonoꞌo rahao ire roga tuḡune buniro.  
\v 14 Aniꞌe butu agireḡa ibiꞌa mazaonoꞌo meiroteꞌe inaraḡa hina butu agireḡa ibiꞌa veize haḡai nu badeḡa haḡairo. Aniꞌe eꞌe haḡaiḡa nu badeḡa hina rahao radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa soꞌosoꞌoziro. Aniꞌa zeḡe mazao ꞌahige rae reiro, “Butu agireḡa ibiꞌa veize ane iraḡa teige haḡairoteꞌe iraḡa ꞌahoga haḡaoꞌi.” Butu agireḡa ibiꞌaꞌe ibite benisionoꞌo idiri boro meiro rehano, bare ḡabodiro.  
\v 15 Butu agireḡa aheuḡaꞌe butu agireḡa ibiꞌa mazaonoꞌo meiroteꞌe inaraḡa hina, butu agireḡa ibiꞌa iraḡa teige haḡairoteꞌe iraḡa ꞌahoga zamaḡano irineḡa haro. ꞌOugadu eꞌe iraḡaniꞌa ḡoeroga idararo, ebu aniꞌa ani mazao mene kurauꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zemoga zuni idararo.  
\v 16 Ebu butu agireḡa aheuḡaniꞌa vaze niduꞌa ibitozeadu zeḡe edaꞌe ꞌevoꞌa rafaḡano ga zehereze rana tahi ꞌahoga mae tiro. Nize komeꞌa zu nize boro, maꞌora zu zahara, tuḡure azaḡa zu mene tuḡure azaḡa niduꞌa tahi eꞌe mae tiro.  
\v 17 Iniu tahi eꞌe mene meiroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡau ꞌahoga hoitoga ga seronogaꞌe mene idararo. Tahi aꞌe butu agireḡa ibiꞌa ni ga niḡa nabaḡa.\f + \fr 13:17 \ft Giriki ḡoeꞌa tibatibaꞌe nabaḡeta. Ni nabaꞌe ni ḡoeꞌa tibatiba niduꞌa meꞌodiroteꞌe nabaḡa. \f*   
\p
\v 18 Nabaḡa eꞌe huga faine ederifine zamarone huhuzaḡa moꞌi. Iniu faine zamareꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe butu agireḡa ibiꞌa ni nabaḡa meꞌode nuroꞌi. Nabaḡa aꞌe vaze ꞌahoga niḡa ihozeꞌohe. Niḡa nabaḡaꞌe 666.   
\c 14  
\s1 Mamoe Ubuga ebu Vaze Niduꞌa 144,000  
\p
\v 1 Ebu hena eꞌa ehamarotene, Sioni maḡano Mamoe Ubuganiꞌa edau radiro. Ebu vaze niduꞌa 144,000 ani teite edau radiro. Zehereze rana Mamoe Ubuga ni zu Moga ni mirihogaꞌe eꞌe.  
\v 2 Ebu e adureonoꞌo ago ꞌahoga igiro. Aꞌe vu boro ḡuhiḡaniꞌa noauꞌeteꞌe teigiro zu viriꞌa ḡihau gudauꞌeteꞌe teigiro. Eꞌa igiroteꞌe agoḡaꞌe gabi arahoḡa azaḡaniꞌa gabize arahohauꞌeteꞌe agoḡa teigiro.  
\v 3 Vaze 144,000 eꞌeꞌa kini ehoro iḡuꞌa zamao, zu ḡaboga ḡauḡa ḡazaḡa zamao, zu ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zamao bada iziga ꞌahoga badahinu. Vaze 144,000 daꞌo bada eꞌe edeḡa. Zeꞌe raha azaḡa boꞌaḡano runeonoꞌo bohaze buziroteꞌe azaḡa.  
\v 4 Zeꞌe roḡae teite mene daroe futaroteꞌe aruꞌaḡa teige, ahirize mene toraneꞌenaꞌa, deheru ꞌaune radiro. Ze Mamoe Ubuganiꞌa noꞌe onamine, ani hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa. Zeꞌe raha azaḡanonoꞌo bohaze buziro ebu ire maḡa ibiꞌa teige, Badiꞌa zu Mamoe Ubuga veize dibuꞌiroteꞌe azaḡa ibiꞌa.  
\v 5 Zeḡe mazao ḡuriro ḡoeꞌani ꞌahogaꞌe oꞌoꞌa, ebu veꞌoḡani ꞌahogaꞌe oꞌoꞌa.   
\s1 Tuḡure Viga Uḡidu  
\p
\v 6 E tuḡure viga ꞌahoganiꞌa adure nemaḡano rafiuꞌeteꞌe horoniro. Aniꞌe rahao radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa, habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa, urabo niduꞌa, ḡoere nunu azaḡa niduꞌa, zu vaze nunu niduꞌa mazao haramoga veize radiu tuḡutuḡu hariḡa manoḡa mae ariro.  
\v 7 Ani ḡihau huauꞌenaꞌa, ꞌahige rae reiro, “Badiꞌa gubanoꞌi ebu niḡa mae ḡihinoꞌi. Mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa kotaziteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa feureha. Adure, raha, davara zu vu nunu niduꞌa haḡairoteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa mazao kuranoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 8 Ebu hena ani ḡaruna tuḡure viga aheuḡaniꞌa hegotadu ꞌahige rae reiro, “Higaneha! Ne boro bagaḡa, Babuloniaꞌe higaneha! Aꞌe daro fuꞌa roḡaeḡa heuḡa. Ani habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa tutuzadu ze vaini vuḡa sauꞌa bagaḡa gagiro zu ani teite daro fuꞌa haḡairo.”   
\p
\v 9 Ebu hena zeḡe ḡaruna tuḡure viga uḡiduḡaniꞌa hegotadu ago boro hina ꞌahige rae reiro, “Iniu butu agireḡa zu ane iraḡa teige haḡairoteꞌe iraḡa mazao kurauꞌenaꞌa, zeherezeo ga ꞌevoreze rafaḡano ani tahi maꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe,  
\v 10 Badiꞌa zama ḡugi teigeꞌeteꞌe vainiḡa vuḡa gagiꞌuma. Vaini vuḡa aꞌe vu teite mene mirunadu ufeta riḡa, ebu Badiꞌa zama ḡugiꞌa bioḡano beꞌuniro. Ebu ze tuḡure viga zaḡoḡa zu Mamoe Ubuga zamao ire roga zu sulifu uꞌano, gigiꞌa boro hidiꞌuma.  
\v 11 Gigiꞌa boro ziniꞌeteꞌe ire rogaḡa ḡisiḡaꞌe ḡisaꞌuma onamo tuḡutuḡu. Butu agireḡa zu ane iraḡa teige haḡairoteꞌe iraḡa mazao kurauꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ga ane ni tahiḡa maꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe, ohere zu madaio ahirize ohonogaꞌe mene idaraꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 12 Eꞌanoꞌo Badiꞌa mone azaḡa, zaeꞌa Badiꞌa goro ḡoeꞌa hegoteꞌeteꞌea, zu Iesu mazao fie obone giganeꞌeteꞌea, zamaze obone gigane huniꞌuma.   
\p
\v 13 Ebu hena e adureonoꞌo ago ꞌahoganiꞌa ꞌahige raꞌeteꞌe igiro, “ꞋAhi mirihoꞌi: Izidi onamo iḡaiḡa Zuhiꞌa Boro teite tiburanadu radiuꞌenaꞌa rudauꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa manohuga hideꞌohe.” Badiꞌa Vineꞌa ꞌahige naenaeneꞌohe, “Oꞌe, ze zeḡe gauonoꞌo bohatanadu ahirize ohoniꞌuma, mazaḡa ze zeḡe haḡai manoḡa naeḡa hidiꞌuma.”   
\s1 Rahao Hiriviro  
\p
\v 14 Ebu hena e ehamarotene, ḡoze ꞌuruḡa ꞌahogaꞌe eꞌe. Ḡoze eꞌe rana Vaze Ubuga heuḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa ehore radiro. Ani vadinioꞌe golo hina haḡairoteꞌe kini vadini adiriḡa ridiro zu benisi eꞌaḡa oboniro.  
\v 15 Ebu hena tuḡure viga ꞌahoganiꞌa kuru neḡanonoꞌo buau aradu ḡoze rana ehore radiuꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa mazao ago boro hina ꞌahige huau ḡoeriro, “Benisiḡo madu hirivoꞌi, mazaḡa rahao hiriviteꞌe ogomuḡaꞌe hiḡudadu hiriveꞌeteꞌe madaḡaꞌe feureha.”  
\v 16 Eꞌanoꞌo ḡoze rana ehore radiuꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa benisiḡa raha rana masiniro ebu raha ogomuḡa hiriviro.   
\p
\v 17 Ebu hena tuḡure viga ꞌahoganiꞌa adureo kuru neḡanonoꞌo buau ariro ebu ani zuni benisiḡa eꞌaḡa oboniro.  
\v 18 Ebu hena tuḡure viga ꞌahoganiꞌa dibuꞌo fataḡanonoꞌo ariro. Aniꞌe dibuꞌo fataḡa rana ire roga taufeꞌeteꞌe inaraḡa meiro. Aniꞌa ago boro hina benisi eꞌaḡa meiroteꞌe tuḡureḡa viga mazao ꞌahige huaro, “Benisiḡo eꞌaḡa madu rahao vaini ireḡanonoꞌo vaini eꞌoḡa nu nuꞌonoꞌi, mazaḡa vaini maḡamaḡaꞌe hiḡudeha.”  
\v 19 Eꞌanoꞌo tuḡure viganiꞌa raha rana benisiḡa hina masinadu vaini maḡamaḡa mae nuꞌoniro, ebu vaini maḡamaḡa moꞌinadu vaini vuḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe iduḡa boro bagaḡa zamaḡano feuniro. Aꞌe Badiꞌa zama ḡugiꞌa ihozeꞌohe.  
\v 20 Vaini vuḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe iduḡaꞌe ne boro ḡabiri biriḡa ibihetaḡano haḡairo. Idu eꞌe zamaḡano vaini maḡamaḡa rana edanadu moinirotene, idu eꞌeanoꞌo ruꞌa sore buaro. Ruꞌe ufeta boro hune soronadu vu boro teigiro. Ruꞌe hosi hebe miniḡa hanini itiro zu 300 kilomita faḡa sore onamiro.   
\c 15  
\s1 Tuḡure Vigaviganiꞌa Ḡonaga Adugaḡa Boro Odohe Ariro  
\p
\v 1 Ebu hena e adureo zaguzagatiteꞌe haḡaiḡa nu badeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa ꞌahoga horoniro. Tuḡure viga fuꞌo aheu fareꞌa aduga boro fuꞌo aheu fare meiro. Aꞌe aduga boro ḡonaga, mazaḡa eꞌe adugaḡaniꞌa hauḡine Badiꞌa zama ḡugiḡaniꞌa ḡonabiꞌuma.   
\p
\v 2 Ebu e galasi hina haḡairoteꞌe davaraḡa ire roga teite tiburanoga teigiroteꞌe horoniro. Zuni vaze nuꞌa galasi davaraḡa genaḡano edauꞌeteꞌe horoziro. Zeꞌe butu agireḡa zu ane iraḡa teige haḡairoteꞌe iraḡa zu ane ni nabaḡa raharahaziroteꞌe azaḡa. Zeꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa ziniroteꞌe gabiḡa obone edau radiro.  
\v 3 Ebu ze Badiꞌa tuḡure vazeḡa Mose bada zu Mamoe Ubuga bada badahiro,  
\q1 “Zuhiꞌa Boro Badiꞌa Gigiꞌaḡa,  
\q2 haḡaiḡoꞌe ḡihiꞌaḡa,  
\q2 zu vazeꞌa horonadu zaguzagauꞌohe.  
\q1 Ḡaꞌe habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa Kini,  
\q2 ibiḡoꞌe duduḡa zu huga.   
\q1
\v 4 Zuhiꞌa Boro, iniuꞌa ḡa mene rihoꞌiꞌuma?  
\q2 Zu iniuꞌa niḡo mene mae ḡihiniꞌuma?  
\q1 Ḡae tibuhugaꞌe zaḡoḡa.  
\q1 Habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa ḡae vaḡe ariꞌuma,  
\q2 zu ḡae mazao kuraꞌuma,  
\q1 mazaḡa ḡae haḡai duduḡaniꞌa fureraro.”   
\p
\v 5 Eꞌe enogano e ehamarotene, adureo kuru neḡa vavaꞌiro. Aꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa ane mone azaḡa teite radiroteꞌe dibuꞌoḡa taruhaḡa heuḡa.  
\v 6 Aduga boro fuꞌo aheu fare meiroteꞌe tuḡureḡa viga fuꞌo aheu fareꞌa kuru neḡanonoꞌo buau ariro. Zeꞌe dabua deheḡa manoḡa zu vazavazahoga vidaro, ebu golo miniḡa uꞌunizeo abiriro.  
\v 7 Ebu hena ḡaboga ḡauḡa ḡazaḡa boꞌaḡano ꞌahoganiꞌa golo hina haḡairoteꞌe siuvaḡa fuꞌo aheu fareꞌe tuḡure viga fuꞌo aheu fare ziniro. Siuva eꞌe zamaḡanoꞌe radiu tuḡutuḡu Badiꞌaḡa zama ḡugiꞌaḡaniꞌa iri'aviro.  
\v 8 Ebu Badiꞌa ni ḡihiꞌaḡanonoꞌo zu gigiꞌaḡanonoꞌo ḡisiꞌa buanadu kuru neḡa zamaḡano iriꞌaviro. ꞌOugadu vazeni ꞌahoganiꞌa kuru neḡa zamaḡano diuḡogaꞌe mene idararo, onamo tuḡure viga fuꞌo aheu fareꞌa odoheꞌeteꞌe adugaḡa boro fuꞌo aheu fareꞌa ḡonabiꞌuma.   
\c 16  
\s1 Badiꞌa Zama Ḡugi Ufiroteꞌe Siuvaḡa  
\p
\v 1 Ebu hena e kuru neḡanonoꞌo ago boro ꞌahoga igiro. Ago eꞌeꞌa tuḡure viga fuꞌo aheu fare ꞌahige rae ziro, “Onamadu Badiꞌa zama ḡugi ufiroteꞌe siuvaḡa fuꞌo aheu fare rahao beꞌunoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 2 Eꞌanoꞌo tuḡure viga ibiꞌaniꞌa onamadu ane siuva rahao beꞌuniro. ꞌOugadu idiri ḡiḡaroḡa zu gigiꞌaḡaniꞌa iniu butu agireḡa tahi meiroteꞌe azaḡa zu ane iraḡa teige haḡairoteꞌe iraḡa mazao kuraroteꞌe azaḡa rana fureraro.   
\p
\v 3 Tuḡure viga aheuḡaniꞌa ane siuva davarao beꞌuniro. ꞌOugadu davaraꞌe rune vazeḡa ru teige nufiro, ebu davarao radiuꞌeteꞌe ḡaboga ḡauḡa niduꞌaꞌe rudau hauḡiro.   
\p
\v 4 Tuḡure viga uḡiduḡaniꞌa ane siuva vu boro zamaḡano zu idu vuḡano beꞌunadu vu niduꞌaꞌe ruo reiro.  
\v 5 Ebu e vu taufeꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa viganiꞌa ꞌahige raꞌeteꞌe igiro,  
\q1 “Badiꞌa Zaḡoḡa, ḡaꞌe izidi radiuꞌeteꞌe zu ibite radiroteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa.  
\q2 Ḡaeꞌa ꞌouge ze kotazirotaꞌaꞌe duduḡa.   
\q1
\v 6 Zeꞌa ḡae mone zaḡoḡa azaḡa zu peroveta azaḡa zemadu ruze soroniroteꞌe uꞌano,  
\q2 ḡaeꞌa ru ze gagoziniro.  
\q1 ꞌOuge zeꞌa haḡaize sauꞌa naeḡa mougaꞌe duduḡa hune.”   
\m
\v 7 Ebu e ago ꞌahoga dibuꞌo fataḡanonoꞌo ꞌahige naenaeniroteꞌe igiro, “Oꞌe, Zuhiꞌa Boro Badiꞌa Gigiꞌaḡa, ḡae kotaꞌe huga zu duduḡa.”   
\p
\v 8 Ebu hena tuḡure viga ḡazaḡaḡaniꞌa ane siuva mada rana beꞌuniro. Ebu madaꞌa ire roga hina vaze iriꞌeteꞌe inaraḡa Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo meiro.  
\v 9 ꞌOugadu zeꞌe mada gigiꞌa bagaḡaniꞌa iri haoziro. Rehano zeꞌa aduga eꞌe ibitohauꞌeteꞌe inaraḡa meiroteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa niḡa rae sausauniro. Ze zamaze ḡihunoga zu Badiꞌa ni mae ḡihinoga hezahoharo.   
\p
\v 10 Ebu hena tuḡure viga fuꞌoḡaniꞌa ane siuva butu agireḡa kiniḡa ehoro iḡuꞌano beꞌuniro. ꞌOugadu butu agireḡaniꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe habaꞌa niduꞌa uzaboraro. Vaze idirizeꞌa ufeta gigizadu ze mazaneze vihoniro.  
\v 11 Zeḡe gigiꞌa zu idiri uꞌano ze adureo Badiꞌa rae sausauniro. Ebu ze zeḡeꞌa haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa moneo mene ḡihuriro.   
\p
\v 12 Ebu hena tuḡure viga fuꞌo tiba fareḡaniꞌa ane siuva vu boro ꞌahoga, niḡa Euferate rana beꞌuniro. ꞌOugirotene, vuꞌa revaranadu madaꞌa iteꞌeteꞌe moneonoꞌo kiniḡakiniḡa ibi ruhibiro.  
\v 13 Ebu e vine toraga uḡidu feḡoza heuḡa horoziro. Zeꞌe isona horeḡa hebeonoꞌo zu butu agireḡa hebeonoꞌo zu ḡuriro peroveta vazeḡaonoꞌo bua ariro.  
\v 14 Zeꞌe vine sauꞌa. Ze haḡai nu badeḡa haḡaeꞌenaꞌa, raha niduꞌa zamaḡano kini niduꞌa vaḡe ragaveꞌohe. Ze Gigiꞌa Badiꞌaḡa mada boro meiteꞌe madaḡano fureratiteꞌe utiḡa veize raha kiniḡa niduꞌa nuꞌozifine ꞌouge ragaveꞌohe.   
\p
\v 15 Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa ꞌahige raꞌohe, “Ḡianoꞌi, e ḡonore vazeḡa teige ariꞌuma! Iniu evate radiuꞌenaꞌa, ane dabua taufeꞌeteꞌe zu firina mene ragaveꞌeteꞌe zu vaze ubumao mazagaro mene fureneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe matuꞌiꞌuma.”  
\v 16 Ebu hena vine sauꞌa uḡiduꞌa kini niduꞌaꞌe haba ꞌahogano nuꞌoziro. Haba niḡaꞌe Heberu ḡoeꞌano Aramagedono rae huniro.   
\p
\v 17 Tuḡure viga fuꞌo aheu fareḡaniꞌa ane siuva hitanao beꞌuniro. ꞌOugirotene, adureo kuru neḡa zamaḡano kini ehoro iḡuꞌanonoꞌo ago boro ꞌahoganiꞌa buanadu ꞌahige rae reiro, “Gau niduꞌa haḡae hauḡeha!”  
\v 18 Ebu agaḡaniꞌa vazavazahiro, zu ago boroꞌa fureraro, zu viriꞌa fuꞌuriro, zu rahaꞌa borofe hagariro. Vazeꞌa rahao radiroteꞌeanoꞌo onao izidi rahaꞌa ꞌouge borofe hagariroteꞌe mene horoniro.  
\v 19 Ne boro bagaḡa, Babuloniaꞌa varadanadu uḡiduo reiro, ebu habaꞌahabaꞌa neḡa boroboroꞌa higaro. Badiꞌaꞌa ne boro bagaḡa, Babulonia azaḡa haḡai sauꞌa zamariro, eꞌanoꞌo ane zama ḡugiꞌa boro hune beꞌune iriꞌavoniroteꞌe vaini vuḡa bioḡa ziniro.  
\v 20 Rahaꞌa borofe hagariro ꞌahine, ꞌumu niduꞌaꞌe dauḡiro ebu maḡamaḡa zuni mene bare horoniro.  
\v 21 Ebu adureonoꞌo ḡoze hatuꞌaḡaniꞌa vaze rana buaro. Ḡoze hatuꞌaḡa tiba adugaꞌe nariga 50 kilo heuḡa. Ḡoze hatuꞌaḡa uꞌano aduga ufeta riḡa bagaḡa hidiro ꞌahine, ze Badiꞌa rae sausauniro.   
\c 17  
\s1 Roḡae Daro Fuꞌa zu Butu Agireḡa  
\p
\v 1 Badiꞌa zama ḡugi iriꞌavoniroteꞌe siuvaḡa fuꞌo aheu fare meiroteꞌe tuḡureḡa viga fuꞌo aheu fare boꞌaḡano ꞌahoganiꞌa eḡe vaḡe aradu ꞌahige rae reiro, “Aroꞌi, eḡeꞌa vu boro ḡehaḡa genaḡano ne boro bagaḡaniꞌa aduga hiditeꞌe moneo ihoꞌiꞌuma. Ne boro aꞌe roḡae daro fuꞌa bagaḡa heuḡa.  
\v 2 Raha kiniḡakiniḡaniꞌa roḡae eꞌe teite daroe futaro ebu rahao radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ane vaini vuḡa gagadu ane daro fuꞌa haḡaiḡa hegotiro.”   
\p
\v 3 Ebu Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa eḡe rana reirotene, eḡe tutuhe haba bohaꞌa onamiro. Eꞌea roḡae ꞌahoganiꞌa butu agireḡa kanaḡa rana ehoreꞌeteꞌe horoniro. Butu agireḡa ahiꞌa ranaꞌe Badiꞌa ni rae sausauneꞌeteꞌe niḡaniḡa mirihoganiꞌa iriꞌaviro. Ebu vadiga niduꞌaꞌe fuꞌo aheu fare zu araḡa niduꞌaꞌe gaubanana.  
\v 4 Roḡae aꞌe dabua peporoḡa zu kanaḡa vidaro, ebu golo zu naeḡa boro hadiḡa nunu ebu gudugudu naeḡa boro hina rohorohoniro. Ani ꞌevoꞌano golo bioḡa oboniro. Bio zamaḡanoꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa heꞌeheꞌeneꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa zu ane daro fuꞌa toraganiꞌa iriꞌaviro.  
\v 5 Zehereḡanoꞌe ni ꞌahoga mirihoga eꞌe. Ni eꞌe hugaꞌe ꞌuꞌuruḡa. Aꞌe ꞌahige rae mirihiro,  
\pc “Ne Boro Bagaḡa Babulonia,  
\pc Daro Fuꞌa Roḡaeḡaroḡaeḡa Vize,  
\pc Rahao Badiꞌaꞌa Heꞌeheꞌeneꞌeteꞌe Ḡauḡa Niduꞌa Vize.”   
\m
\v 6 E roḡae aꞌe gagone fuꞌa horoniro. Aniꞌa Badiꞌa mone azaḡa ruze ufeta gagiro. Zeꞌe Iesu moneo rae fureniroteꞌe azaḡa.  
\p E roḡae eꞌe horonadu zaguzagau rudaro.  
\v 7 Rehano tuḡure viganiꞌa ꞌahige ihiro, “Ḡa nougadu zaguzagauꞌohe? Eḡeꞌa roḡae eꞌe moneo ꞌuꞌuru touga ihoꞌiꞌuma. Ebu aniꞌa ehoreꞌeteꞌe butu agireḡa moneo ꞌuꞌuru touga ihoꞌiꞌuma. Butu agireḡa vadigaꞌe fuꞌo aheu fare zu araḡaꞌe gaubanana.  
\v 8 Ḡaeꞌa horoniroteꞌe butu agireḡaꞌe ibite radiro, rehano izidiꞌe oꞌoꞌa. Aniꞌa vesuꞌu idu vo huneonoꞌo\f + \fr 17:8 \fqa Abisi \f* bua eradu Badiꞌaꞌa ani ruine hauḡiꞌuma. Rahao radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano nuꞌa ani horonadu zaguzagaꞌuma. Zeꞌe raha zu adure haḡairoteꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo iniu ḡaboziteꞌe azaḡa nize mirihiroteꞌe bukaḡano nize oꞌoꞌa azaḡa. Butu agireḡa aꞌe ibite radiro, rehano izidi oꞌoꞌa, ebu vesuꞌu ariteꞌe uꞌano, ze ani horonadu zaguzagaꞌuma.   
\p
\v 9 Zamarone huhuzaḡa hina faine zamare huniꞌuma. Butu agireḡa vadiga fuꞌo aheu fareꞌe roḡae eꞌeꞌa ehoreꞌeteꞌe maḡaḡa fuꞌo aheu fareo idaniro.  
\v 10 Zuni maḡamaḡa aꞌe kini fuꞌo aheu fareo idaniro. Kini fuꞌoꞌe rudaro, rehano ꞌahogaꞌe radiuꞌohe. Ebu ꞌahogaꞌe ꞌize mene areha, rehano aniꞌa arine mada tahiḡa daꞌo radiꞌuma.  
\v 11 Ibite radiro rehano, izidi mene radiuꞌeteꞌe butu agireḡaꞌe kini fuꞌo uḡidu fareḡa rae reꞌuma. Aniꞌe ibite kini fuꞌo aheu fare boꞌaḡano ꞌahoga, ebu Badiꞌaꞌa ruine huniꞌuma.   
\p
\v 12 Ḡaeꞌa horoniroteꞌe araḡa gaubananaꞌe kini gaubananao idaniro. Ze ꞌize raha azaḡa zuhiꞌaziteꞌe mene ḡadahiro, rehano butu agireḡa eꞌe teite zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe kiniḡa inaraḡa mada tahiḡa daꞌo meꞌuma.  
\v 13 Ze zamaze tibano inaraze zu gigiꞌaze butu agireḡa haꞌuma.  
\v 14 Ze zu butu agireḡaꞌe Mamoe Ubuga utitohaꞌuma, rehano Mamoe Ubuganiꞌa zeḡe niduꞌa raharahaziꞌuma. Mazaḡa aniꞌe zuhiꞌa niduꞌa vitizeꞌeteꞌe Zuhiꞌaḡa Boro zu kini niduꞌa vitizeꞌeteꞌe Kiniḡa. Mamoe Ubuga ḡatineꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Mamoe Ubuganiꞌa huziroteꞌe zu ohotiroteꞌe azaḡa. Zeꞌe zamaze niduꞌa hina ani hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa.”   
\p
\v 15 Ebu tuḡure viga eꞌeꞌa ꞌahige ihiro, “Ḡaeꞌa roḡae daro fuꞌa eꞌeꞌa vu boro ḡehaḡa genaḡano ehore radiroteꞌe horoniro. Vu boro aꞌe vaze nunu, vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa nunu, habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa nunu, zu ḡoere nunu azaḡano idaziro.  
\v 16 Ḡaꞌa horoniroteꞌe butu agireḡa zu araḡa gaubananaꞌe roḡae daro fuꞌa heꞌeheꞌeniꞌuma. Zeꞌe ani ruiniꞌuma zu firinohaꞌuma. Ze ani modare aꞌuma zu ire roga hina hufi haoniꞌuma.  
\v 17 Mazaḡa zeꞌa ꞌouge haḡaoga veize Badiꞌaꞌa zamarone ꞌuguḡa zamazeo tiro. Eꞌanoꞌo ze Badiꞌa ura haḡaiꞌuma, ebu ze zeḡeꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe inaraḡaꞌe butu agireḡa eꞌe haꞌuma rae ḡoere idaniꞌuma, onamo Badiꞌa ḡoereꞌa hudaꞌuma.  
\v 18 Ḡaeꞌa horoniroteꞌe roḡaeḡaꞌe ne boro bagaḡa eꞌe. Ne boro bagaḡa eꞌeꞌa raha kiniḡakiniḡa zuhiꞌaziꞌohe.”   
\c 18  
\s1 Babuloniaꞌe Higaro  
\p
\v 1 Eꞌe enogano, e tuḡure viga ꞌahoganiꞌa adureonoꞌo ovaoga horoniro. Aniꞌe inara boro meiro. Ani agaḡaꞌe vazavazahoga uꞌano raha niduꞌa aganiro.  
\v 2 Aniꞌa ago boro hina ꞌahige huau ḡoeriro, “Higaneha! Ne boro bagaḡa, Babuloniaꞌa higaneha! Aniꞌe Diabolo radone habaꞌa reiro, zu vine sauꞌa toraga niduꞌa neḡa reiro, ebu vazeꞌa heꞌeheꞌezeꞌeteꞌe niniḡa toraga niduꞌa neḡa reiro.  
\v 3 Mazaḡa habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa Babuloniaꞌa ziniroteꞌe vainiḡa vuḡa riḡa gagadu ani teite daroe futaro. Raha kiniḡa niduꞌa ani teite daroe futaro ebu rahao serosereꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe maꞌorao reiro, mazaḡa Babuloniaꞌa hadi naeḡa boroboro ḡauḡa ufeta hoitiro.”   
\p
\v 4 Ebu hena e adureonoꞌo ago ꞌahoganiꞌa ꞌahige raꞌeteꞌe igiro,  
\q1 “Eḡe vaze niduꞌa, Babulonia neḡanonoꞌo buanoꞌi.  
\q2 ꞌOugine zaeꞌa ani haḡai sauꞌa mene hegotiꞌuma,  
\q2 zu aniꞌa hiditeꞌe adugaḡa za mene hidiꞌuma.   
\q1
\v 5 Mazaḡa ani haḡai sauꞌaꞌe gudiru itadu adure haniniro.  
\q2 Badiꞌaꞌa ani haḡai sauꞌa zamareꞌohe.   
\q1
\v 6 Ne boro eꞌeꞌa zae sausauziroteꞌe idunaḡano zaeꞌa eꞌe naeḡa baronohanoꞌi.  
\q2 Ne boro eꞌeꞌa haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa idunaḡano, eꞌe naeḡa ḡae aheu ufeta ragate baronohanoꞌi.  
\q1 Ne boro eꞌeꞌa aduga hideꞌeteꞌe bioḡa zae ziniro.  
\q2 Eꞌanoꞌo zaꞌe aduga ḡae aheu ufeta ragate hiditeꞌe bioḡa hanoꞌi.   
\q1
\v 7 Ne boro eꞌeꞌa niḡa mae ḡihiniro zu hadi naeḡa boroboro hoiteꞌenaꞌa matuꞌe radiro.  
\q2 Eꞌanoꞌo haḡaiḡa eꞌe idunaḡano gigiꞌa zu zama aroga hanoꞌi.  
\q1 Ne boro eꞌeꞌa zamao ꞌahige raꞌohe,  
\q2 'E kini roḡaeḡa radu vaze zuhiꞌaziꞌohe.  
\q2 E mene ḡozoba.  
\q2 Eꞌanoꞌo zamahe mene hune ariꞌuma.'   
\q1
\v 8 Eꞌanoꞌo mada tiba zamaḡano ne boro eꞌe aduga boro hidiꞌuma,  
\q2 rune hidiꞌuma, zamaḡa aradu niaꞌuma, zaga hidiꞌuma,  
\q1 ebu ire roga hina hufi haoniꞌuma.  
\q2 Mazaḡa ne boro eꞌe kotaneꞌeteꞌe Zuhiꞌaḡa Boro Badiꞌaḡaꞌe gigiꞌa hune.   
\p
\v 9 Raha kiniḡa niduꞌaꞌe ne boro eꞌe teite daro futaro, zu naeḡa boroboro ḡauḡa hoiteꞌenaꞌa matuꞌe radiro. Ze ne boro eꞌe hufi haoneꞌeteꞌe ire rogaḡa ḡisiḡa horonadu niau kuaꞌuma.  
\v 10 Zeꞌe ne boro eꞌeꞌa hideꞌeteꞌe adugaḡa rihoneꞌenaꞌa, faḡano edanadu ꞌahige reꞌuma,  
\q1 'Aduga boro hideha,  
\q2 Ne boro ḡihiꞌaḡa, ne boro inaraḡa,  
\q2 Babulonia, aduga boro hideha!  
\q1 Mada tahiḡa fase zamaḡano Badiꞌaꞌa ḡa ruiꞌeha.'   
\p
\v 11 Rahao serosereꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ani uꞌano niau ḡoinahiꞌuma, mazaḡa zeḡe mazaonoꞌo ḡau ꞌahoga bare hoititeꞌe azaḡani ꞌahoga oꞌoꞌa.  
\v 12 Zeḡeꞌa seroniroteꞌe ḡauḡaꞌe golo, siliva, naeḡa boro hadiḡa, gudugudu naeḡa boro, dabua manoḡa tauḡi, dabua peporoḡa, dabua vazavazahoga, dabua kanaḡa, ire hohoḡa nunu, elefaniti ḡonoga hina haḡairoteꞌe ḡauḡa naeḡa boro nunu, naeḡa boro ireḡa nunu, kopa zu auri zu hadi manomano hina haḡairoteꞌe ḡauḡa nunu,  
\v 13 iniga zu naeḡa boro niḡa Sinamono,\f + \fr 18:13 \ft Aꞌe ire ꞌahoganonoꞌo haḡaeꞌohe. Hohoḡa iniga hune zu naeḡa boro. \f* eḡa nunu, ꞌuvahu hohoḡa, murava hohoḡa, dehoro hohoḡa, vaini vuḡa, olivi dehoroḡa, ꞌuvahu zu vuidi, boromakau zu mamoe, hosi zu hosi kiuḡa. Ze vaze zuni tuḡure azaḡano seroziro. \fig Elefaniti|src="67_Rev18:12_DH-ElephantTusks.tif" size="col" ref="18:12" \fig*   
\p
\v 14 Ḡau ꞌuguḡa seroniroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ne boro eꞌe mazao ꞌahige reꞌuma, 'Ḡaeꞌa meihi rae urate huniroteꞌe ḡauḡa manoḡa niduꞌaꞌe dauḡeha. Ḡau ḡehaḡa niduꞌa zu naeḡa boroboro ḡauḡa niduꞌa ḡae mazaonoꞌo dauḡadu ꞌuguḡa mene bare horoniꞌuma!'  
\v 15 ꞌUguḡa ḡauḡa ne boro eꞌe azaḡa mazao seronadu maꞌorao reiroteꞌe serosero azaḡaꞌe ne boro eꞌeꞌa aduga boro hidirotaꞌaꞌe rihonadu faḡano edauꞌenaꞌa, niau ḡoinahiꞌuma. Ebu ze ꞌahige reꞌuma,   
\q1
\v 16 'Aduga boro hideha! Ne boro ḡihiꞌaḡa, aduga boro hideha!  
\q2 Aniꞌa dabua manoḡa tauḡi, dabua peporoḡa zu kanaḡa vidaudo,  
\q2 ebu golo, hadi naeḡa boro nunu zu gudugudu naeḡa boro hina rohorohido.   
\q1
\v 17 Rehano mada tahiḡa fase zamaḡano ḡau ḡehaḡa niduꞌa aꞌe ruiniro!'  
\p Ḡasi boro azaḡa, ḡasi boro zamaḡano tiriroteꞌe azaḡa, ḡasi boro gau azaḡa ebu davarao gaueꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa faḡano edaꞌuma.  
\v 18 Zeꞌa ne boro eꞌe hofoga ḡisiḡa horonirotene, agoze boro hina ꞌahige huau ḡoeriꞌuma, 'Ne boro ꞌahiguḡa heuḡa neḡa ꞌahogaꞌe oꞌoꞌa hune!'  
\v 19 Ebu ze zeḡeꞌa bare kono vadinizeo feuniꞌuma,\f + \fr 18:19 \ft Iuda azaḡa haḡai. Ze ufeta zama areꞌeteꞌe ihozifine, ꞌouge haḡaeꞌohe. \f* ebu niau ḡoinaheꞌenaꞌa, ꞌahige ḡihau huaꞌuma,  
\q1 'Aduga boro hideha! Ne boro ḡihiꞌaḡa, aduga boro hideha!  
\q2 Ḡasi boro hina davarao ḡau nunu seroniroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe maꞌorao reiro,  
\q2 mazaḡa ne boro eꞌeꞌa hadi boro hina zeḡe ḡau hoitido.  
\q1 Rehano mada tahiḡa fase zamaḡano ne boro eꞌe ruineha!   
\q1
\v 20 Adureo radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, ne boro ꞌai ruiniro ꞌahine, matuꞌoꞌi,  
\q1 Badiꞌa mone azaḡa, apostolo azaḡa zu peroveta azaḡa, matuꞌoꞌi,  
\q2 mazaḡa ne boro eꞌeꞌa zae sausauziroteꞌe uꞌano, Badiꞌaꞌa zae veize ne boro eꞌe kotaniro.'”   
\p
\v 21 Ebu hena tuḡure viga gigiꞌaḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa vuidi duine seꞌeneꞌeteꞌe hadiḡa boro bagaḡa heuḡa hadiḡa boro ꞌahoga mae ḡihinadu davarao feuniro, ebu ꞌahige rae reiro,  
\q1 “Hadi boro ꞌahi ḡihau feuniroteꞌe teige,  
\q2 ne boro ḡihiꞌaḡa, Babulonia mae feuniꞌuma,  
\q2 ebu ne boro eꞌe mene bare horoniꞌuma.   
\q1
\v 22 Gabi vaꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, bada maꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, suraꞌi hudiꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu bigoro hudiꞌeteꞌe azaḡa agoꞌe  
\q2 ne boro eꞌe zamaḡano mene bare igiꞌuma.  
\q1 Ḡau nunu haḡaeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ne boro eꞌe zamaḡano  
\q2 mene bare horoziꞌuma,  
\q1 vuidi duine seꞌeneꞌeteꞌe hadiḡa boro bagaḡa agoḡaꞌe ne boro eꞌe zamaḡano  
\q2 mene bare igiꞌuma.   
\q1
\v 23 Ihure agaḡaꞌe ne boro eꞌe zamaḡano  
\q2 mene bare agaraꞌuma,  
\q1 hahu iziga ohozeḡa zu roḡaeḡa agozeꞌe ne boro eꞌe zamaḡano  
\q2 mene bare igiꞌuma.  
\q1 Mazaḡa ne boro eꞌe mone serosereꞌeteꞌe azaḡa inaraꞌe raha ꞌadao ufeta boro hune reiro,  
\q2 ebu ne boro eꞌeꞌa murava haḡaiḡa hina habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa soꞌosoꞌoziro.   
\q1
\v 24 Ne boro eꞌe zamaḡano peroveta azaḡa zu Badiꞌa mone azaḡa ruze,  
\q2 ebu rahao zimiroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa ruzeꞌe horoniro.”   
\c 19  
\s1 Adureo Badiꞌa Niguneꞌohe  
\p
\v 1 Eꞌe enogano e adureo vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa huauꞌeteꞌe teige, ago boro igiro. Ze ꞌahige rae huaro,  
\q1 “Haleluia!  
\q1 Emeḡe Badiꞌaꞌa ḡabofiro. Aniꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune zu gigiꞌa hune.   
\q2
\v 2 Ane kotaꞌe huga zu duduḡa.  
\q1 Raha azaḡa tutuzadu daro fuꞌa haḡaiḡa ibiḡano  
\q2 sausauziroteꞌe roḡaeḡa daro fuꞌa eꞌe kotaniro.  
\q1 Roḡae eꞌeꞌa Badiꞌa tuḡure azaḡa zemadu ruzeꞌa soriro ꞌahine,  
\q2 Badiꞌaꞌa roḡae eꞌe naeḡa baronoharo.”   
\m
\v 3 Ebu adureo vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa bare ꞌahige rae huaro,  
\q1 “Haleluia!  
\q1 Ne boro eꞌeanoꞌo ire roga ḡisiḡaniꞌa iteꞌohe onamo radiu tuḡutuḡu.”   
\m
\v 4 Ekalesia ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa 24 zu ḡaboga ḡauḡa ḡazaḡaniꞌa ḡuḡuradu kini ehoro iḡuꞌano ehoreꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa mazao kuraro, ebu ꞌahige rae reiro,  
\q1 “Amen, Haleluia!”   
\p
\v 5 Ebu kini ehoro iḡuꞌanonoꞌo ago ꞌahoganiꞌa bua aradu ꞌahige rae reiro,  
\q1 “Badiꞌa tuḡure azaḡa niduꞌa  
\q2 zu ani gubaneꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa  
\q1 ebu ni komeꞌa zu ni boro azaḡa niduꞌa,  
\q2 emeḡe Badiꞌa nigunoꞌi!”   
\p
\v 6 Ebu hena e vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa ḡoereꞌeteꞌe teige ago ꞌahoga igiro. Ago aꞌe vu boro ḡuhiḡaniꞌa noauꞌeteꞌe teigiro zu viriꞌa borofe fuꞌureꞌeteꞌe teigiro. Ago eꞌeꞌa ꞌahige huaro,  
\q1 “Haleluia!  
\q2 Zuhiꞌa Boro emeḡe Badiꞌa Gigiꞌaḡaniꞌa ḡau niduꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌohe.   
\q1
\v 7 Matuꞌe rudatihi  
\q2 zu ane ni mae ḡihinihi.  
\q1 Mazaḡa Mamoe Ubuga hahu madaḡa ꞌai feureha  
\q2 zu ane hahu roḡaeḡa izigaꞌe aneꞌa bare rohorohonadu ruhibeha.   
\q1
\v 8 Badiꞌaꞌa dabua deheḡa manoḡa vazavazahoga  
\q2 ane hahu roḡaeḡa iziganiꞌa vidanoga veize haro.”  
\m Dabua manoḡa tauḡiꞌe Badiꞌa mone azaḡa haḡai duduḡa rae idaneꞌohe.   
\p
\v 9 Ebu tuḡure viganiꞌa ihiro, “ꞌAhige mirihoꞌi: Mamoe Ubuga mui zamaḡano huziroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe matuꞌe rudauꞌohe.” Ebu bare ꞌahige ihiro, “Aꞌe Badiꞌa ḡoere huga.”  
\v 10 Ebu hena e ani mazao kuratihi radu odaḡa babaḡano ḡuḡuriro, rehano ani ihiro, “Ago ꞌougoꞌi! Eḡe zuni ḡa ebu ḡae nego nabudi heuḡa tuḡure vazeḡa, ebu emeꞌe Iesu moneo rae fureneꞌeteꞌe azaḡa. Badiꞌa mazao kuranoꞌi, mazaḡa Iesu moneo rae fureneꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa rae fureneꞌohe.”   
\s1 Hosi ꞌUruḡano Ehoreꞌeteꞌe Vazeḡa  
\p
\v 11 E adure vavaꞌoga horonirotene hosi ꞌuruḡa ꞌahoga eꞌe. Ebu vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa hosi eꞌe rana ehore radiro. Ani niꞌe Zama Niduꞌa Hina Haḡaoga, zu Huga. Aniꞌa ibi duduḡano kotazeꞌohe ebu utiteꞌohe.  
\v 12 Ani ubumaꞌe ire roga duhuḡa heuḡa ebu vadigano kini vadini adiriḡa ḡehaḡa ridiro. Ebu ahiꞌa ranaꞌe ni mirihoga ꞌahoga eꞌe. Vazeni ꞌahoga zuni ni eꞌe aḡuꞌa, rehano ane daꞌo edeḡa.  
\v 13 Aniꞌe dabua ruḡeta vidaro, ebu ani niꞌe Badiꞌa Ḡoere.  
\v 14 Adure uti azaḡaniꞌa hosi ꞌuruḡa rana ehoradu ani hegotinu. Zeꞌe dabua deheḡa manoḡa tauḡi vidaro.  
\v 15 Ani hebeonoꞌoꞌe benisi eꞌaḡaniꞌa buanadu habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa ruiziꞌuma, ebu aniꞌa auri somoriḡa gigiꞌaḡa hina zuhiꞌaziꞌuma. Vazeꞌa vaini vuḡa haḡaifine vaini maḡamaḡa rana edanadu moineꞌeteꞌe teige, aniꞌa agire azaḡa edeze ḡahiziꞌuma. Badiꞌa Gigiꞌaḡa zama ḡugiꞌaꞌe boro hune ꞌahine, ꞌouge aduga ziniꞌuma.  
\v 16 Ane dabua zu maniganoꞌe ni ꞌahoga ꞌahige rae mirihiro, 'Kini Niduꞌa Kiniḡa zu Zuhiꞌa Niduꞌa Zuhiꞌaḡa.'   
\p
\v 17 Ebu hena e tuḡure viga ꞌahoganiꞌa mada rana edanoga horoniro. Aniꞌa hitana huneo rafiuꞌeteꞌe niniḡa niduꞌa mazao ago boro hina ꞌahige ḡihau ḡoeriro, “Aroꞌi. Badiꞌa mui boro veize nuꞌoranoꞌi.  
\v 18 Kini azaḡa, uti azaḡa boroboro, vaze inarazeta, hosi zu eꞌe rana ehoriroteꞌe azaḡa, tuḡure azaḡa niduꞌa zu mene tuḡure azaḡa niduꞌa, nize komeꞌa zu nize boro azaḡa rune ahiri modareze anoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 19 Ebu hena e butu agireḡa zu raha kiniḡa azaḡa zu zeḡe uti azaḡaniꞌa hosi ꞌuruḡa rana ehoriroteꞌe vazeḡa zu ane uti azaḡa teite utitoga veize nuꞌoraroteꞌe horoziro.  
\v 20 Rehano hosi ꞌuruḡa rana ehoriroteꞌe vazeḡa zu ane uti azaḡaniꞌa butu agireḡa obone tiro, ebu butu agireḡa mone edanadu haḡai nu badeḡa haḡairoteꞌe ḡuriro peroveta vazeḡa zuni ani teite oboze tiro. Peroveta vazeḡa aꞌe haḡai nu badeḡa haḡadu butu agireḡaonoꞌo tahi meiroteꞌe azaḡa zu butu agireḡa iraḡa teige haḡairoteꞌe iraḡa mazao kuraroteꞌe azaḡa soꞌosoꞌoziroteꞌe vazeḡa. Hosi ꞌuruḡa rana ehoriroteꞌe vazeḡa zu ane uti azaḡaniꞌa butu agireḡa zu ḡuriro peroveta vazeḡaꞌe ḡabona oboze teadu sulifu hina hufiꞌeteꞌe ire rogaḡa duꞌuraḡano feuziro.  
\v 21 U iniu ire roga duꞌuraḡano mene feuziroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe hosi rana ehoriroteꞌe vazeḡa hebeonoꞌo buaroteꞌe benisiḡa hina zimiro, ebu nini niduꞌaꞌe rune ahiri modareze anadu isize miniro.   
\c 20  
\s1 Muri 1000  
\p
\v 1 Ebu hena e tuḡure viga ꞌahoganiꞌa adureonoꞌo ovaoga horoniro. Aniꞌa idu vo hune vavaꞌeꞌeteꞌe kiḡa zu auri adiriḡa boro ꞌevoꞌano oboniro.  
\v 2 Aniꞌa isona horeḡa eꞌe obone tiro. Isona horeḡa aꞌe Diabolo ga Satani, ebu ibite hune radiu onainuteꞌe moheḡa. Tuḡure viganiꞌa isona horeḡa eꞌe auri adiriḡa boro hina susadu muri 1,000 zamaḡano obone tiro.  
\v 3 Aneꞌa idu vo huneo isona horeḡa eꞌe mae feunadu ibihetaḡa hararo ebu vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa mene vavaꞌoga veize ibihetaḡa ꞌuiro. Aꞌe isona horeḡa eꞌeꞌa habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa mene soꞌozifine raꞌohe, onamo muri 1,000 ḡonaga. Eꞌe enogano ani mae bunadu mada tahiḡa radiꞌuma.   
\p
\v 4 Ebu hena e kini ehoro iḡuꞌano ehoreꞌeteꞌe azaḡa horoziro. Zeꞌe kotazeꞌeteꞌe inaraḡa Badiꞌaꞌa ziniroteꞌe azaḡa. Ebu e vaze vine nu horoziro. Zeꞌe Iesu moneo rae fureniro zu Badiꞌa ḡoere rae fureniro ꞌahine, vadinize variꞌe modiroteꞌe azaḡa. Zeꞌe butu agireḡa zu ane iraḡa teige haḡairoteꞌe iraḡa mazao mene kuraro, ebu zeherezeo zu ꞌevoreze rafaḡano butu agireḡa tahi mene meiro. Zeꞌe ḡabodadu Keriso teite muri 1,000 zamaḡano ḡau niduꞌa zuhiꞌaziro.  
\v 5 (Rune azaḡa nuꞌe mene ḡabodiro onamo muri 1,000 ḡonaga meiro.) Aꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa rune azaḡa bare ḡaboziroteꞌe madaḡa ibiꞌa.  
\v 6 Badiꞌaꞌa rune azaḡa bare ḡaboziroteꞌe madaḡa ibiꞌaḡano bare ḡabodiroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe zaḡoḡa zu matuꞌe rudauꞌohe. Rune aheuḡaniꞌa ze zuhiꞌaziteꞌe inaraḡaꞌe oꞌoꞌa. Zeꞌe Badiꞌa zu Keriso veize gaueꞌeteꞌe dibuꞌoḡa azaḡano reꞌuma ebu Keriso teite muri 1,000 zuhiꞌaziꞌuma.   
\s1 Satani Ruiniꞌuma  
\p
\v 7 Muri 1,000 enogano Sataniꞌe ane ḡuꞌa neḡanonoꞌo mae buniꞌuma.  
\v 8 Aniꞌa buanadu raha niduꞌa zamaḡano avoavo radiuꞌeteꞌe habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa soꞌozoga veize onamiꞌuma. Eꞌe habaꞌahabaꞌa nizeꞌe Goga zu Magoga. Sataniꞌe uti veize ze nuꞌoziꞌuma ebu zeḡe niduꞌaꞌe davara niꞌuriḡa teige ḡeharaꞌuma.  
\v 9 Zeꞌe raha naenae niduꞌa oname hauḡadu Badiꞌa mone azaḡa radone habaꞌa zu Badiꞌa zamarone neḡa boro merau ꞌuiro. Rehano ire rogaꞌa adureonoꞌo ovadu ze hufi haoziro.  
\v 10 Ze soꞌoziroteꞌe Diaboloḡa zuni sulifu hina hufi haoneꞌeteꞌe ire roga duꞌuraḡano mae feuniro. Ire rogaḡa duꞌuraḡa aꞌe butu agireḡa zu ḡuriro peroveta vazeḡaniꞌa radiuꞌeteꞌe habaꞌa. Deꞌea ze ohere zu madai gigiꞌa boro meꞌuma onamo tuḡutuḡu.   
\s1 Rune Azaḡa Kotaziꞌuma  
\p
\v 11 Ebu hena e kini ehoro iḡuꞌa ꞌuruḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa ebu eꞌe rana ehoriroteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa horoniro. Ani zamao raha zu adureꞌa dauḡadu iḡurize mene bare horoniro.  
\v 12 Ebu e rune azaḡa, nize boro zu nize komeꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa kini ehoro iḡuꞌa eꞌe zamao edauꞌeteꞌe horoziro. Ebu buka nu vavaꞌiro, aꞌe rune azaḡaniꞌa haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa niduꞌa mirihiroteꞌe bukaḡa. Ebu buka ꞌahoga zuni vavaꞌiro, aꞌe ḡaboziteꞌe azaḡa nize mirihiroteꞌe bukaḡa. Rune azaḡaꞌe buka nu eꞌe zamaḡano mirihiroteꞌe teige, ze haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa idunaḡano kotaziro.  
\v 13 Davarao rudaroteꞌe azaḡa zuni kini ehoro iḡuꞌa zamao edaro. Ebu rudanadu rune azaḡa habao\f + \fr 20:13 \fqa Hadesi \f* radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zuni kini ehoro iḡuꞌa zamao edaro. Ebu zeḡe niduꞌa zeꞌa haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa idunaḡano kotaziro.  
\v 14 Ebu hena rune azaḡa zu zeḡe radone habaꞌaꞌe ire roga duꞌuraḡano mae feuziro. Ire roga duꞌuraḡaꞌe rune aheuḡa.  
\v 15 Iniu ḡaboziteꞌe azaḡa nize mirihiroteꞌe bukaḡano niḡa oꞌoꞌa vazeḡaꞌe ire roga duꞌuraḡano mae feuniro.   
\c 21  
\s1 Adure Iziga zu Raha Iziga  
\p
\v 1 Ebu hena e adure iziga zu raha iziga horoniro. Adure ibiꞌa zu raha ibiꞌa ꞌai dauḡiro ebu davara zuni mene bare horoniro.  
\v 2 Ebu e ne boro zaḡoḡa, Ierusalema iziganiꞌa adureonoꞌo Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo ovaoga horoniro. Aniꞌe hahu iziga roḡaeḡaniꞌa iꞌa veize faine rohorohadu ruhibiroteꞌe teige manoḡa tauḡi.  
\v 3 Ebu e kini ehoro iḡuꞌanonoꞌo ago boro ꞌahoganiꞌa ꞌahige raꞌeteꞌe igiro, “Ḡianoꞌi, Badiꞌa radone habaꞌaꞌe vaze boꞌaḡano eꞌe. Aniꞌe zeḡe teite radiꞌuma. Zeꞌe ani mone azaḡa rae reꞌuma, ebu aniꞌe aneꞌa bare zeḡe teite radiꞌuma, ebu aniꞌe zeḡe Badiꞌa rae reꞌuma.  
\v 4 Aniꞌa zeḡe ni vuḡa niduꞌa ubumazeo zauhiꞌuma. Runeꞌe mene bare fureraꞌuma. Zamaze aroga, nianoga zu gigiꞌa zuni mene bare fureraꞌuma, mazaḡa ḡau amahiḡa niduꞌa dauḡiro.”   
\p
\v 5 Ebu kini ehoro iḡuꞌano ehoriroteꞌe Badiꞌaḡaniꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, “Ḡianoꞌi, eḡeꞌa ḡau niduꞌa izife haḡaeꞌohe.” Ebu ani bare ꞌahige rae reiro, “ꞌAhi mirihoꞌi, mazaḡa ḡoere ꞌahiꞌe huga ebu vaze niduꞌa mae ḡihiniteꞌe ḡoeꞌa.”  
\v 6 Ebu ani bare ꞌahige ihiro, “Eḡeꞌa ꞌahi niduꞌa haḡae hauḡeha! Eꞌe Alefa zu Omega, ḡadaheḡa zu ḡonaga. Iniu iriga moꞌoneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡeꞌa ḡaboneꞌeteꞌe iduḡa vuḡa naeḡa oꞌoꞌa haꞌuma.  
\v 7 Iniu sauꞌa ḡauḡa raharahaneꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe eꞌeguḡa niduꞌa eḡeꞌa ziniꞌuma. Eꞌe zeḡe Badiꞌa rae reꞌuma ebu zeḡe niduꞌaꞌe eḡe ubude rae reꞌuma.  
\v 8 Rehano riho fuꞌa azaḡa, mene fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, Badiꞌaꞌa heꞌeheꞌeneꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, vaze mauꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, daro fuꞌa azaḡa, murava azaḡa, ḡuriro badiꞌaḡa mazao kurauꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, zu ḡuriro azaḡa niduꞌa—zeḡe niduꞌa radone habaꞌaꞌe ire roga zu sulifu hina hufi haozeꞌeteꞌe duꞌuraḡa rae reꞌuma. Aꞌe rune aheuḡa.” \fig Tuḡure viganiꞌa Ierusalema ne boro udaheꞌohe|src="MH-AngelMeasures1.png" size="col" ref="21:8" \fig*   
\s1 Ierusalema Iziga  
\p
\v 9 Ḡonaga adugaḡa boro fuꞌo aheu fare ufiroteꞌe siuvaḡa fuꞌo aheu fare meiroteꞌe tuḡureḡa viga fuꞌo aheu fare boꞌaḡano ꞌahoganiꞌa eḡe vaḡe aradu ꞌahige ihiro, “Aroi, eꞌa Mamoe Ubuga inuga, hahu iziga roḡaeḡa ihoꞌiꞌuma.”  
\v 10 Ebu Vine Zaḡoḡaꞌe eḡe rana radiroteꞌe zamaḡano, tuḡure viga eꞌeꞌa eḡe zamahadu maḡa boro bagaḡa zu hitana hune itiro. Ebu adureonoꞌo Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo ovaeꞌeteꞌe neḡa boro zaḡoḡa, Ierusalema ihohiro.  
\v 11 Ne boro aꞌe Badiꞌaonoꞌo agaḡa boro ꞌahine, agaru deheraro. Aꞌe naeḡa boro hadiḡa ꞌuruḡa, niḡa iasipa teige agararo, ebu galasi teige deheḡa bagaḡa.  
\v 12 Ne boro aꞌe ḡabiri boro hitaga hina meraro zu ibihetaḡa niduꞌaꞌe gaubanana aheu fare. Ibiheta niduꞌao tuḡure viga gaubanana aheu fareꞌa edaro ebu ibiheta eꞌe ranaꞌe Isaraela urabo nize gaubanana aheu fare mirihiro.  
\v 13 Ibiheta uḡiduꞌe madaꞌa iteꞌeteꞌe moneo, zu ibiheta uḡiduꞌe madaꞌa zubureꞌeteꞌe moneo, zu ibiheta uḡiduꞌe naeḡano,\f + \fr 21:13 \ft south\f* zu ibiheta uḡiduꞌe naeḡano\f + \fr 21:13 \ft north\f* eꞌe.  
\v 14 Ne boro ḡabiriḡaꞌe hadi boro gaubanana aheu fare rana ogoraro, ebu hadi eꞌe niduꞌa ranaꞌe Mamoe Ubuga apostolo azaḡa gaubanana aheu fare nize gaubanana aheu fare mirihiro.   
\p
\v 15 Eḡe teite ḡoeriroteꞌe tuḡureḡa vigaꞌe ne boro eꞌe zu ibihetaḡa zu ḡabiriḡa udahoga veize golo hina haḡairoteꞌe somoriḡa ꞌahoga meiro.  
\v 16 Ne boro eꞌe genaḡa ḡazaḡa mone niduꞌaꞌe idaḡa radu faḡa zu rafaḡaꞌe tiba. Aniꞌa udaho somoriḡa hina ne boro eꞌe udahirotene, faḡaꞌe 2,200 kilomita, ebu rafaḡa zu hitaga zuni tiba.  
\v 17 Aniꞌa ne boro ḡabiriḡa hitaga udahirotene, aꞌe 66 mita. Aꞌe vazeꞌa ḡau udaheꞌeteꞌe ibiḡano udahiro ebu tuḡure viga zuni eꞌe ibiḡano udahiro.  
\v 18 Ḡabiriḡaꞌe naeḡa boro hadiḡa ꞌuruḡa niḡa iasipa hina ogoranadu agararo zu deheḡa bagaḡa galasiḡa heuḡa goloḡa huga hina ogoraro.  
\v 19 Ne boro ḡabiriḡaꞌe hadi boroboro rana ohoniro, ebu hadi boro niduꞌaꞌe naeḡa boro hadiḡa nunu hina rohorohoniro: Hadi boro ibiꞌaꞌe naeḡa boro hadiḡa ꞌuruḡa niḡa iasipa, hadi boro aheuḡaꞌe naeḡa boro hadiḡa buluḡa niḡa safaia, hadi boro uḡiduḡaꞌe naeḡa boro hadiḡa ḡabodoraḡa niḡa kalekedoni, hadi boro ḡazaḡaḡaꞌe naeḡa boro hadiḡa ḡabodoraḡa niḡa samaragi,  
\v 20 hadi boro fuꞌoḡaꞌe naeḡa boro hadiḡa barauniḡa zu ꞌuruḡa niḡa onisi, hadi boro fuꞌo tiba fareḡaꞌe naeḡa boro hadiḡa kanaḡa niḡa sadio, hadi boro fuꞌo aheu fareḡaꞌe naeḡa boro hadiḡa boraḡa niḡa kurusolito, hadi boro fuꞌo uḡidu fareḡaꞌe naeḡa boro hadiḡa ḡabodoraḡa niḡa berulo, hadi boro fuꞌo ḡazaḡa fareḡaꞌe naeḡa boro hadiḡa boraḡa niḡa topazo, hadi boro gaubananaḡaꞌe naeḡa boro hadiḡa ḡabodoraḡa niḡa kurusoparaso, hadi boro gaubanana tiba fareḡaꞌe naeḡa boro hadiḡa buluḡa niḡa iasinito, ebu hadi boro gaubanana aheu fareḡaꞌe naeḡa boro hadiḡa peporoḡa niḡa ametuso hina rohorohoniro.  
\v 21 Ibihetaḡa gaubanana aheu fareꞌe gudugudu naeḡa boro gaubanana aheu fare hina haḡairo, ebu ibihetaḡa tibatibaꞌe gudugudu naeḡa boro tiba hina haḡairo. Ne boro ibiḡa boroꞌe galasi deheḡa bagaḡa teige golo huga hina haḡairo.   
\p
\v 22 E ne boro eꞌe zamaḡano kuru neḡa mene horoniro, mazaḡa Zuhiꞌa Boro Badiꞌa Gigiꞌaḡa zu Mamoe Ubuganiꞌa ne boro eꞌe zamaḡano radadu kuru neḡa teigiro.  
\v 23 Ne boro eꞌe zamaḡano madaꞌa ga batoꞌa agaranoga mene urateꞌohe, mazaḡa Badiꞌa agaḡaniꞌa ne boro eꞌe aganeꞌohe zu Mamoe Ubugaꞌe ihure radu aganeꞌohe.  
\v 24 Habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡaniꞌa ne boro agaḡano radiꞌuma, ebu raha kiniḡakiniḡaniꞌa zeḡe ḡau manomano madu ne boro eꞌe ariꞌuma.  
\v 25 Deꞌea ohere oꞌoꞌa ꞌahine, mada niduꞌa ibiheta mene ꞌuiꞌuma.  
\v 26 Habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡaniꞌa ḡau ḡihiꞌaḡa zu ḡau manomano madu ne boro eꞌe ariꞌuma.  
\v 27 Mene deheḡa ḡauḡa niduꞌaꞌe ne boro eꞌe diuḡoga mene idaraꞌuma, ebu mazagaro haḡaiḡa zu soꞌosoꞌo haḡaiḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zuni diuḡoga mene idaraꞌuma. Rehano iniu Mamoe Ubuganiꞌa ḡaboziteꞌe azaḡa nize mirihiroteꞌe bukaḡano nize eꞌe azaḡaniꞌa daꞌo diuḡoga idaraꞌuma.   
\c 22  
\s1 Ḡabone Ziniꞌeteꞌe Vuḡa Boro  
\p
\v 1 Ebu hena tuḡure viganiꞌa ḡaboziteꞌe vuḡa boro ihohiro. Aꞌe galasi deheḡa bagaḡa teige agararo. Vu boro eꞌeꞌa Badiꞌa zu Mamoe Ubuga kini ehoro iḡuꞌanonoꞌo sore buaro,  
\v 2 ebu ne boro ibiḡa boro nemaḡa sore onamiro. Vu boro naenaeoꞌe ḡabone ziniꞌeteꞌe ireḡa eꞌe. Ire eꞌe maḡa iraḡa nunuꞌe gaubanana aheu fare, ebu maḡa tibatibaꞌe bato tibatiba zamaḡano hudauꞌohe. Eꞌe ireḡa rouḡaꞌe habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa ugionoꞌo manozeꞌohe.  
\v 3 Ne boro eꞌe zamaḡanoꞌe radiu tuḡutuḡu adugaḡa mene bare hidiꞌuma. Eꞌea Badiꞌa zu Mamoe Ubuga kini ehoro iḡuꞌa eꞌe, ebu Badiꞌa tuḡure azaḡaniꞌa ani mazao kuraꞌuma.  
\v 4 Zeꞌe Badiꞌa iraḡa horoniꞌuma ebu Badiꞌa niꞌe zehereze ranao mirihiꞌuma.  
\v 5 Eꞌea ohereꞌe mene bare horoniꞌuma, ebu ihure ga mada agaḡa mene uratiꞌuma, mazaḡa Zuhiꞌa Boro Badiꞌaꞌa agaḡa ziniꞌuma. Ebu zeꞌe ḡau niduꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌuma onamo tuḡutuḡu.   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ariꞌuma  
\p
\v 6 Tuḡure viganiꞌa ꞌahige ihiro, “Ḡoere ꞌahi niduꞌaꞌe ḡoere huga zu vazeꞌa mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa. Zuhiꞌa Boro Badiꞌaꞌa ane Vine peroveta azaḡa ziniꞌohe. Ani naginiꞌa ḡarihe fureratiteꞌe moneo ane tuḡure azaḡa ihozifine ane tuḡure viga tuḡuniro.”  
\v 7 Iesuꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, “Ḡianoꞌi, e ḡarihe ariꞌuma! Buka ꞌahi zamaḡano irina rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa hegoteꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe matuꞌeꞌohe.”   
\p
\v 8 Eḡe, Ioaneꞌa ꞌahi niduꞌa igiro zu horoniroteꞌe vazeḡa. Eḡeꞌa ꞌahi niduꞌa igiro zu horonirotene, eꞌe ihohiroteꞌe tuḡureḡa viga mazao kuranoga veize odaḡa babaḡano ḡuḡuriro.  
\v 9 Rehano aniꞌa ꞌahige ihiro, “Ago ꞌougoꞌi! Eḡe zuni ḡa ebu peroveta azaḡa ebu ꞌahi bukaḡano mirihiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa teite gau tiba haḡaeꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa vazeḡa. Badiꞌa mazao daꞌo kuranoꞌi!”  
\v 10 Ebu aniꞌa ꞌahige ihiro, “Buka ꞌahi zamaḡano irina rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ago ꞌuꞌuru toꞌi, mazaḡa ꞌuguḡa ḡoeꞌaniꞌa fureratiteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa haniteha.  
\v 11 Iniu sauꞌa vazeḡaꞌe haḡai sauꞌa haḡaeꞌenaꞌa radiu onamoꞌi, ebu toraga vazeḡaꞌe haḡai toraga haḡaeꞌenaꞌa radiu onamoꞌi. Iniu duduḡa vazeḡaꞌe haḡai duduḡa haḡaeꞌenaꞌa radiu onamoꞌi, ebu zaḡoḡa vazeḡaꞌe zaḡozaḡe radiu onamoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 12 Iesuꞌa ꞌahige raꞌohe, “Ḡianoꞌi, e ḡarihe ariꞌuma. Vaze niduꞌa zeḡeꞌa haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa idunaḡano naeze baronoziniꞌuma.  
\v 13 Eꞌe Alefa zu Omega, ibiꞌa zu ḡonaga, ḡadaheḡa zu ḡonaga raꞌohe.   
\p
\v 14 Iniu dabuaze vuzuꞌeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe matuꞌeꞌohe. Ze ḡaboneziniꞌeteꞌe ireḡa vaḡe onamoga zu ne boro ibihetaḡanonoꞌo ne boro zamaḡa diuḡogaꞌe idaḡa reꞌuma.  
\v 15 Rehano ḡuni heuḡa toraga azaḡa, murava azaḡa, daro fuꞌa azaḡa, vaze mauꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, ḡuriro badiꞌaḡa mazao kurauꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, ḡuriro zamaradu ḡurire haḡaeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe ne boro enoneo radiꞌuma.   
\p
\v 16 Eꞌe Iesu. E ekalesia azaḡa, zae mazao eḡe tuḡure viga tuḡunadu aniꞌa eḡe ḡoere ꞌahi ihoziro. Eꞌe kini Davida mariga ḡihiꞌa hune zu irara buzuvaḡa agaḡa.”   
\p
\v 17 Vine Zaḡoḡa zu Badiꞌa mone azaḡa hahu iziga roḡaeḡa teigeꞌeteꞌeꞌa Iesu mazao ꞌahige rae raꞌohe, “Aroꞌi!” Ebu iniu ḡoere ꞌahi igiꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa zuni ꞌahige reꞌuma, “Aroꞌi!” Ebu iniu irineꞌa moꞌoneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa zuni aroꞌi. Iniu uratoꞌidene, ḡabone hauꞌeteꞌe vuḡa, naeḡa oꞌoꞌa ḡahunoneḡa moꞌi.   
\p
\v 18 Iniu buka ꞌahao irina rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa igiꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa mazao e iradugu ḡoeꞌa riḡa ziꞌohe. Iniu buka ꞌahi ḡoeꞌa rana ḡoere ꞌahoga ragate tiꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa buka ꞌahao reiroteꞌe adugaḡa boro haꞌuma.  
\v 19 Ebu iniuꞌa buka ꞌahao irina rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa niduꞌaonoꞌo ḡoere ꞌahoga mae vaḡinine, aniꞌa hiditeꞌe manohugaḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa mene haꞌuma. ꞌOugadu ani ne boro zaḡoḡa diuḡoga mene idaraꞌuma zu ḡabone hatiteꞌe ireḡa maḡa anogaꞌe mene idaraꞌuma.   
\p
\v 20 ꞌAhi niduꞌa rae fureneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, Iesuꞌa ꞌahige raꞌohe, “Hube hune ḡarihe amiꞌuma.”  
\p Amen. Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu, aroꞌi!   
\p
\v 21 Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesuꞌa Badiꞌa mone azaḡa niduꞌa mazao manoḡa fureneꞌenoꞌi. Amen.   